"The user and opponent engage in a mutual exchange of gifts, fostering a "
"brief moment of camaraderie in the midst of battle."

msgid "potluck"
msgstr "Open Mat Special"

msgid "pouch_description"
msgstr ""
"The user refreshes themselves with a tasty morsel from a pouch or bag."

msgid "pouch"
msgstr "Tape Break"

msgid "power_theft_description"
