"The user extends a long, proboscis-like appendage, draining the opponent's "
"life force while inflicting damage."

msgid "proboscis"
msgstr "Collar Drag"

msgid "pseudopod_description"
msgstr "The user extends a pseudopod to deliver a forceful, sticky blow."

msgid "pseudopod"
msgstr "Long Arm Frame"

msgid "punch_description"
msgstr "The user applies a miserable shoulder crossface. Absolutely rude."

msgid "punch"
msgstr "Crossface"

