"The user unleashes a furious barrage of rocks, threatening to overwhelm the "
"opponent with a crushing avalanche of stone."

msgid "rocky_barrage"
msgstr "Pressure Barrage"

msgid "roll_description"
msgstr "The user rolls through danger and scrambles to a better position."

msgid "roll"
msgstr "Granby Roll"

msgid "rot_description"
msgstr "A sickness befalls the target."

msgid "rot"
msgstr "Bad Habits"

msgid "ruby_description"
msgstr ""
"The user fires a concentrated beam of ruby-like energy, inflicting damage."

msgid "ruby"
msgstr "Red Belt Myth"

msgid "rust_bomb_description"
