"A corrosive projectile that explodes on impact, dealing damage and poisoning"
" the opponent."

msgid "rust_bomb"
msgstr "Rusty Technique"

msgid "saber_description"
msgstr "The user strikes with a swift and powerful sword-like attack."

msgid "saber"
msgstr "Slicer Entry"

msgid "salamander_description"
msgstr "A bite brimming with heat and lashing pain."

msgid "salamander"
msgstr "Hot Scramble"

msgid "sand_spray_description"
msgstr ""
"A cloud of abrasive sand is hurled at the opponent, damaging their vision "
"and inflicting damage."

msgid "sand_spray"
msgstr "Dirty Grip Break"

msgid "sands_of_time_description"
