"Heals the user's health by harnessing the energy of a shooting star "
"streaking across the night sky."

msgid "shooting_star_fail"
msgstr "The lack of starlight from the daytime sky prevents the healing."

msgid "shooting_star"
msgstr "Flying Entry"

msgid "shrapnel_description"
msgstr ""
"The user unleashes a barrage of sharp fragments, causing widespread damage."

msgid "shrapnel"
msgstr "Explosive Scramble"

msgid "shuriken_description"
