"The user hurls a deadly array of throwing stars, reinforcing its own resolve"
" with each hit."

msgid "shuriken"
msgstr "Grip Throw"

msgid "sleep_bomb_description"
msgstr ""
"A violent explosion of sleeping powder threatens to send both combatants "
"into a doze."

msgid "sleep_bomb"
msgstr "Nap Trap"

msgid "sleeping_powder_description"
msgstr ""
"A cloud of sleep-inducing pollen is released, causing the opponent to fall "
"asleep."

msgid "sleeping_powder"
msgstr "Sleepy Pressure"

msgid "slice_description"
msgstr "The user wields a sharp blade, delivery a powerful, cutting attack."

msgid "slice"
msgstr "Knee Slice"

msgid "slime_description"
msgstr ""
"A sticky, viscous substance is emitted, engulfing the opponent and dealing "
"damage."

msgid "slime"
msgstr "Sweaty No-Gi"

