"The user unleashes a rain of thorns, shooting a cloud of sharp, piercing "
"projectiles at the opponent, dealing damage and potentially causing the "
"opponent to become stuck, immobilized by the thorny barrage."

msgid "thorn_burst"
msgstr "Painful Frames"

msgid "thunderball_description"
msgstr "With a rumbling like thunder, a hard ball of rock strikes the target."

msgid "thunderball"
msgstr "Blast Shot"

msgid "thunderclap_description"
msgstr ""
"A sudden, deafening clap of thunder that stuns and damages the opponent."

msgid "thunderclap"
msgstr "Heavy Snap Down"

msgid "time_crisis_description"
msgstr "The user distorts the flow of time, causing the opponent damage."

msgid "time_crisis"
msgstr "Stalling Penalty"

msgid "tinder_description"
msgstr "The target is set alight."

msgid "tinder"
msgstr "Warm-Up Round"

msgid "tip_description"
msgstr "The user delivery a swift, precise strike to a vital point."

msgid "tip"
msgstr "Wrist Pick"

msgid "tonguespear_description"
msgstr "The tongue is jabbed into the opponent, and their blood drained."

msgid "tonguespear"
msgstr "Long Range Grip"

msgid "tooth_for_tooth_description"
msgstr "The user bares their fangs, taking pain to give it back."

msgid "tooth_for_tooth"
msgstr "Receipt Given"

msgid "torch_description"
msgstr "A projectile that strikes the opponent."

msgid "torch"
msgstr "Burning Pressure"

msgid "tornado_description"
