"The user summons a swirling vortex of air, unleashing a devastating tornado "
"that lifts the opponent off the ground and deals damage."

msgid "tornado"
msgstr "Tornado Throw"

msgid "trample_description"
msgstr ""
"The user charges at the opponent with a powerful shoulder tackle, knocking "
"them to the ground and then quickly moving away, leaving the target stuck in"
" place."

msgid "trample"
msgstr "Body Lock Trip"

msgid "tsunami_description"
msgstr "The user summons a colossal wave that crashes down upon the opponent."

msgid "tsunami"
msgstr "Wave Sweep"

msgid "tux_attack_description"
msgstr "The user transforms into a whirlwind of data, dealing heavy damage."

msgid "tux_attack"
msgstr "Mascot Smash"

msgid "ubuntu_description"
msgstr ""
"The user emits a chaotic energy that randomly alters the opponent's type."

msgid "ubuntu"
msgstr "Friendly Roll"

msgid "undertaker_description"
msgstr ""
"A desperate, self-sacrificing attack that deals a massive damage at the cost"
" of the user's health."

msgid "undertaker"
msgstr "Bow And Arrow"

msgid "venomous_tentacle_description"
msgstr ""
"A poisonous tentacle strikes the opponent, inflicting damage and poisoning "
"them."

msgid "venomous_tentacle"
msgstr "Leg Entanglement"

msgid "viper_description"
msgstr ""
"The user launches a volley of sharp, wooden darts with incredible speed and "
"accuracy."

msgid "viper"
msgstr "D'Arce Choke"

msgid "vorpal_description"
msgstr ""
"The user unleashes a devastating, precision strike that inflicts severe "
"damage and fills the opponent with a burning desire for revenge."

msgid "vorpal"
msgstr "Clean Submission"

msgid "wall_fire_description"
msgstr ""
"The user conjures a fiery wall that both protects it and scorches the "
"opponent."

msgid "wall_fire"
msgstr "Hot Frame"

msgid "wall_of_steel_description"
msgstr "The user spins about, creating a biting, shielding wall of steel."

msgid "wall_of_steel"
msgstr "Closed Guard"

msgid "wallow_description"
msgstr "The user relaxes in a pool of mud, healing its wounds."

msgid "wallow"
msgstr "Rest Round"

msgid "walls_description"
msgstr ""
"The user constructs sturdy walls of earth or rock to create a defensive "
"barrier."

msgid "walls"
msgstr "Open Guard"

msgid "water_blast_description"
msgstr ""
"The user unleashes a powerful blast of water, striking the opponent with a "
"torrent of liquid force, dealing damage."

msgid "water_blast"
msgstr "Blast Double"

msgid "water_bullet_description"
msgstr "A mouthful of water is flung at the target with great alacrity."

msgid "water_bullet"
msgstr "Quick Shot"

msgid "web_description"
msgstr ""
"A sticky web is shot at the opponent, trapping them and inflicting damage."

msgid "web"
msgstr "Spider Guard"

msgid "webs_wind_description"
msgstr ""
"The user creates a swirling vortex of sticky webs that ensnare the opponent,"
" dealing multiple hits and slowing their movement."

msgid "webs_wind"
msgstr "Lasso Guard"

msgid "whirlwind_description"
msgstr ""
"The user creates a powerful vortex of wind that sweeps the opponent away."

msgid "whirlwind"
msgstr "Granby Escape"

msgid "wicked_wind_description"
msgstr "An ill wind draws near."

msgid "wicked_wind"
msgstr "Nasty Sweep"

msgid "wiggle_description"
msgstr ""
"The user shakes their body back and forth, creating a silly, attention-"
"grabbing display that doesn't do any damage but might be entertaining to "
"watch."

msgid "wiggle_success"
msgstr "{user} wiggled its body!"

msgid "wiggle"
msgstr "Shrimp Escape"

msgid "wing_tip_description"
msgstr "The user delivers a sharp, cutting attack with the tip of its wing."

msgid "wing_tip"
msgstr "Outside Trip"

msgid "woodsmash_description"
msgstr ""
"The user slams into the opponent with a powerful wooden strike, dealing "
"damage and potentially knocking them back."

msgid "woodsmash"
msgstr "Club Grip"

