# Monster details
msgid "aardart_description"
msgstr ""
"It keeps count of every ant it has eaten, and celebrates significant "
"numbers."

msgid "aardart"
msgstr "Bonnie BlueBelt"

msgid "aardorn_description"
msgstr "When born it is placed in an anthill and left to eat its way out."

msgid "aardorn"
msgstr "Vegan Niall"

msgid "abesnaki_description"
msgstr ""
"Each face is a different pattern, and some say the symbols spell out words "
"in a dead language."

msgid "abesnaki"
msgstr "Slutty Sarah"

msgid "agnidon_description"
msgstr ""
"It prefers four legs, but can stand on two to open doors, push over trees or"
" hold things."

msgid "agnidon"
msgstr "Only Dans"

msgid "agnigon_description"
msgstr ""
"It is called a 'false dragon', because it appears to be a dragon, but "
"actually evolved from a different line of ancient reptiles."

msgid "agnigon"
msgstr "Mat Bastard"

msgid "agnite_description"
msgstr "It is playful, but must be taught early on to keep its fire in check."

msgid "agnite"
msgstr "Gi Goblin"

msgid "allagon_description"
msgstr ""
"ALLAGON are drawn to relics made from the metals left behind by their "
"ancestors, and will be violent to retrieve them."

msgid "allagon"
msgstr "Dr Kimura"

msgid "altie_description"
msgstr ""
"ALTIE floated down to earth in a bubble. Now its bubble has popped, it "
"cannot float more than a few meters in the air."

msgid "altie"
msgstr "Coach Atlas"

msgid "ambuwl_description"
msgstr ""
"The egg in its pouch does not hatch. Instead, it secretes a delicious drink "
"with restorative powers."

msgid "ambuwl"
msgstr "Spazzy Steve"

msgid "ampystoma_description"
msgstr ""
"You would think AMPYSTOMA's warning coloration would make ambush impossible,"
" but the murky waters it hunts in obscure it until it is ready to reveal "
"itself. It likes to go on land during thunderstorms."

msgid "ampystoma"
msgstr "Acai Slut"

msgid "angesnow_description"
msgstr ""
"Those who survive getting lost in hostile, icy conditions often mention a "
"mysterious presence guiding them even when the snow is too heavy to see "
"through."

msgid "angesnow"
msgstr "Craig NoGi"

msgid "angrito_description"
msgstr ""
"It cannot understand why humans feel rage and hatred, but ANGRITO feels "
"these urges too."

msgid "angrito"
msgstr "Wristlock Wes"

msgid "anoleaf_description"
msgstr ""
"It considers the plants growing near it to be its brothers and sisters."

msgid "anoleaf"
msgstr "Stinky Gi"

msgid "anu_description"
msgstr "It is said that it enters others' dreams to search for its lost love."

msgid "anu"
msgstr "Nasty Nate"

msgid "apeoro_description"
msgstr ""
"The kings of old used psychic powers to transfer their souls into these "
"golden computing machines. Now they live on, unable to communicate but still"
" dreaming of empires."

msgid "apeoro"
msgstr "Oilcheck Oz"

msgid "araignee_description"
msgstr ""
"Pedants who say all spiders have eight legs are strangely quiet on the case "
"of ARAIGNEE."

msgid "araignee"
msgstr "Leglock Larry"

msgid "arthrobolt_description"
msgstr ""
"It feels uncomfortable commanding its fellow NUT and BOLT, and usually runs "
"away. But then the NUT and BOLT have no one to instruct them."

msgid "arthrobolt"
msgstr "Porrada Paul"

msgid "askylpaws_description"
msgstr ""
"It is an omen of disaster, often appearing in times of great trouble. This "
"has caused others to sometimes blame it for the misfortune."

msgid "askylpaws"
msgstr "Sandbag Sam"

msgid "asudopt_description"
msgstr ""
"According to legend, ASUDOPT created the world and one day will destroy the "
"world. In the meantime, it sets the world's universal laws."

msgid "asudopt"
msgstr "Sweaty Kev"

msgid "av8r_description"
msgstr "If the sun is out, it can fly as far or as high as it likes."

msgid "av8r"
msgstr "Choke Chad"

msgid "axolightl_description"
msgstr ""
"It lights the deep waters with its tail, marking a safe shelter for fish."

msgid "axolightl"
msgstr "Tapout Tim"

msgid "b_ver_1_description"
msgstr ""
"It is designed for all those times you need something to be bitten by a "
"robot."

msgid "b_ver_1"
msgstr "Guard Slag"

msgid "babysnitch_description"
msgstr ""
"The fuming BABYSNITCH will throw itself into the attack, usually with little"
" effect. But beware: if you laugh at its efforts, it will hunt you once it "
"grows into a BADDRSCRATCH."

msgid "babysnitch"
msgstr "Kimura Kev"

msgid "baddrscratch_description"
msgstr ""
"The furious BADDRSCRATCH is a fearsome hunter, and it will not stop in its "
"pursuit of its prey - even in the face of certain death."

msgid "baddrscratch"
msgstr "Mount Mick"

msgid "bamboon_description"
msgstr "It fights with its bamboo staff, which it also uses for balance."

msgid "bamboon"
msgstr "Halfguard Hal"

msgid "banling_description"
msgstr ""
"Each BANLING is waiting for a homeless spirit to nestle in its branches."

msgid "banling"
msgstr "Judo Jake"

msgid "bansaken_description"
msgstr ""
"As twilight hits, the spirits inside BANSAKEN come to life. They like to add"
" naughty children who stay up too late to their number."

msgid "bansaken"
msgstr "Wrestle Dad"

msgid "banvengeance_description"
msgstr ""
"BANVENGEANCE seeks to make its own night by growing new trees from running "
"roots to drown out the light, smothering competing plant life."

msgid "banvengeance"
msgstr "Neck Crank Ned"

msgid "baobaraffe_description"
msgstr ""
"It stores mass amounts of water in its huge body so that it can travel long "
"distances across hot, dry deserts. It will also share water with thirsty "
"creatures. When it has no water stored it is skinny."

msgid "baobaraffe"
msgstr "Buggy Ben"

msgid "baoby_description"
msgstr ""
"They travel from river to river in search of water to drink and store. The "
"leafy ossicones on its head conceal movable points that act similar to a "
"dowsing rod. Many creatures follow BAOBY in droughts."

msgid "baoby"
msgstr "Degen Dan"

msgid "bedoo_description"
msgstr ""
"It swallows its victims whole, forcing them into a deep sleep for a few "
"hours whilst it feasts on their dreams. Often, it will accidentally put "
"their victims into a permanent sleep."

msgid "bedoo"
msgstr "Bluebelt Ben"

msgid "beenstalker_description"
msgstr ""
"What BEENSTALKER lacks in sense and grace, it makes up for in sheer "
"enthusiasm and goodwill. It delights in scaring off vermin, but never "
"harming them."

msgid "beenstalker"
msgstr "Purple Paul"

msgid "bewhich_description"
msgstr ""
"When BEWHICH holds its breath, it can appear as a beautiful - though "
"sinister - human. "

msgid "bewhich"
msgstr "Brownbelt Bert"

msgid "bigfin_description"
msgstr ""
"A whole ecosystem exists on its back, so it tries not to go underwater."

msgid "bigfin"
msgstr "Blackbelt Baz"

msgid "birdee_description"
msgstr ""
"It is omnivorous, but whether it prefers meat or seed depends on its "
"experiences when young."

msgid "birdee"
msgstr "Fake Coach"

msgid "birdling_description"
msgstr ""
"The ignorant believe that it carries its own egg upon its back. It is the "
"guard for a far more important egg than that."

msgid "birdling"
msgstr "Trial Tony"

msgid "bishosand_description"
msgstr ""
"BISHOSAND is fascinated by religious or spiritual symbols it sees and likes "
"to collect them, but is believed to not understand any of them."

msgid "bishosand"
msgstr "Creonte Carl"

msgid "blasdoor_description"
msgstr ""
"BLASDOOR shield those they care about behind their impenetrable bulk, but "
"macerate unwanted intruders and scrap machines between their steel teeth."

msgid "blasdoor"
msgstr "Manky Mike"

msgid "bolt_description"
msgstr ""
"The presence of a BOLT makes a NUT clamp down harder and spark more energy."

msgid "bolt"
msgstr "Spicy Steve"

msgid "boltnu_description"
msgstr ""
"It spends most of its time digging burrows into the ground, it remains dizzy"
" from the constant vibrations and movement caused by them digging into the "
"soil."

msgid "boltnu"
msgstr "Gassy Gaz"

msgid "botbot_description"
msgstr "It is a universal robot that can be adapted for any purpose."

msgid "botbot"
msgstr "Toehold Tom"

msgid "boxali_description"
msgstr ""
"With its long blue cape, BOXALI can glide above the ground - allowing it to "
"perform stunts and aerial attacks."

msgid "boxali"
msgstr "RNC Ray"

msgid "boxorox_description"
msgstr "The dumber it gets, the harder its rocky body becomes."

msgid "boxorox"
msgstr "Smash Pass Sam"

msgid "brachifor_description"
msgstr "BRACHIFOR can go without eating if it stays perfectly still."

msgid "brachifor"
msgstr "Juice Josh"

msgid "breem_description"
msgstr ""
"It punctures fruit to place new DUGGOT in them by night. By day it pretends "
"to be a normal bee."

msgid "breem"
msgstr "Cringe Craig"

msgid "brewdin_description"
msgstr ""
"Born in neglected, once prized, pottery and similar treasures. Rumored to "
"grants wishes to those who can make it smile."

msgid "brewdin"
msgstr "Lazy Larry"

msgid "bricgard_description"
msgstr ""
"When the winter comes, IMBRICKCILE builds a defensive cocoon of bricks to "
"protect it from predators."

msgid "bricgard"
msgstr "Dojo Derek"

msgid "brickhemoth_description"
msgstr ""
"Be wary when kicking a BRICGARD's nest, because percussive force is the "
"trigger the tuxemon needs to burst forth once it has formed into a "
"BRICKHEMOTH."

msgid "brickhemoth"
msgstr "Shark Tank Sam"

msgid "brumi_description"
msgstr "Neglected brooms may be stolen by BRUMI. "

msgid "brumi"
msgstr "Nosebeer Neil"

msgid "budaye_description"
msgstr ""
"It can convince any group to cooperate for the common good with some "
"encouraging mewls and waves."

msgid "budaye"
msgstr "Kneeride Kev"

msgid "bugnin_description"
msgstr ""
"Its sword is actually an antenna grown and snapped off for that purpose."

msgid "bugnin"
msgstr "Pullguard Pat"

msgid "bumbulus_description"
msgstr ""
"BUMBULUS is a flying being that produces a cloud of smoke to disguise itself"
" as a cloud. No one has ever seen its true body."

msgid "bumbulus"
msgstr "Dirty Dan"

msgid "burrlock_description"
msgstr ""
"BURRLOCK likes to stick to passerbys to help it spread from place to place."

msgid "burrlock"
msgstr "Tap Daddy"

msgid "bursa_description"
msgstr "It rejects fire as basic, and produces only the fire of the mind."

msgid "bursa"
msgstr "Gym Thot"

msgid "cacaburr_description"
msgstr ""
"CACABURR supports many pollinators like TUMBLEBEE and seed lovers like "
"CHICKADEE."

msgid "cacaburr"
msgstr "Acai Addict"

msgid "cackleen_description"
msgstr ""
"Some say CACKLEEN is a possessed child, others that is the lost spirit of a "
"girl. "

msgid "cackleen"
msgstr "Blue Belt Ex"

msgid "cairfrey_description"
msgstr ""
"A jolly piece of furniture who awoke one morning and decided to explore."

msgid "cairfrey"
msgstr "Guard Goblin"

msgid "caper_description"
msgstr ""
"CAPER play and frolic with each other among the foam of mountain rivers, "
"cold as ice."

msgid "caper"
msgstr "Leglock Luke"

msgid "capinyah_description"
msgstr ""
"Only after intense training in the jungles, lifting logs and river boulders,"
" can CAPITI graduate to become CAPINYAH."

msgid "capinyah"
msgstr "Wristlock Will"

msgid "capiti_description"
msgstr ""
"It looks like a baby, but some specimens have been found that are hundreds "
"of years old."

msgid "capiti"
msgstr "Mat Enforcer"

msgid "carcharock_description"
msgstr ""
"CARCHAROCK's ancient instincts are at odds with the modern world, where the "
"scent of PHARFAN and the roar of PANTHERAFIRA have replaced the familiar "
"sounds of its homeland."

msgid "carcharock"
msgstr "Purple Perve"

msgid "cardiling_description"
msgstr "One wouldn't expect it to breathe fire, until it does."

msgid "cardiling"
msgstr "Coach Creepy"

msgid "cardinale_description"
msgstr ""
"It hates all predators with a passion, and makes war with them and their "
"young when it can."

msgid "cardinale"
msgstr "NoGi Niall"

msgid "cardiwing_description"
msgstr "Its song is remarkable, but few dare keep an explosive songbird."

msgid "cardiwing"
msgstr "Trial Guy"

msgid "cataspike_description"
msgstr ""
"It learns to fight from observation. Left to its own devices, it uses its "
"spike to pick up rubbish."

msgid "cataspike"
msgstr "Whitebelt Will"

msgid "cateye_description"
msgstr "They say it blinks once a year, in honor of summer's end."

msgid "cateye"
msgstr "Brownbelt Ben"

msgid "chenipode_description"
msgstr "It bites onto shoelaces and trouser legs when it wants to travel."

msgid "chenipode"
msgstr "Blackbelt Bob"

msgid "cherubat_description"
msgstr ""
"These inquisitive bats are drawn by the heady emotions of people in love, "
"and carry back unsupervised bouquets and chocolate boxes to build their "
"nests."

msgid "cherubat"
msgstr "Darce Dave"

msgid "chibiro_description"
msgstr ""
"It is found in forests and fields, where it is often mistaken for a turnip."

msgid "chibiro"
msgstr "Guillo Gary"

msgid "chickadee_description"
msgstr ""
"CHICKADEE gives longer repeated cries of 'dees' if the danger it senses "
"seems lesser than another."

msgid "chickadee"
msgstr "Armbar Andy"

msgid "chillimp_description"
msgstr ""
"It is rumored to live atop snowy mountains, but no clear photo of it has "
"ever been taken."

msgid "chillimp"
msgstr "Triangle Tom"

msgid "chloragon_description"
msgstr ""
"It hatches when an ancient egg is planted in fertile soil. When the eggs run"
" out, there will be no more CHLORAGON."

msgid "chloragon"
msgstr "Berimbolo Ben"

msgid "chromeye_description"
msgstr "CHROMEYE was created to observe and learn how humans think and feel."

msgid "chromeye"
msgstr "Sambo Sam"

msgid "claymorior_description"
msgstr ""
"It is said that only one in a thousand can rule over the CLAYMORIOR as a "
"REGALANCE."

msgid "claymorior"
msgstr "Judo Judas"

msgid "coaldiak_description"
msgstr "This bear can set fire to anywhere and draw blood from anything."

msgid "coaldiak"
msgstr "Panic Pete"

msgid "cobarett_description"
msgstr ""
"It covers itself in thick, billowing smoke so that it can slide easily "
"through thick brush. The source of the smoke is its molten body temperature,"
" which is so hot that tongues of flame shoot from its mouth."

msgid "cobarett"
msgstr "Sweat Goblin"

msgid "cochini_description"
msgstr ""
"It is as intelligent and aware as a three-year old child. It tastes "
"delicious."

msgid "cochini"
msgstr "Tape Finger"

msgid "cocrune_description"
msgstr "Whichever way it turns, the blood-red eye faces you."

msgid "cocrune"
msgstr "Cauli Carl"

msgid "cohldrabi_description"
msgstr ""
"It is born underground in cold, snowy areas, and learns how to fly within a "
"few weeks."

msgid "cohldrabi"
msgstr "Shit Gi Sean"

msgid "coleorus_description"
msgstr "It has existed, unchanged, for millions of years."

msgid "coleorus"
msgstr "Toe Hold Ted"

msgid "conglolem_description"
msgstr "The gel has long ago dried out, but CONGLOLEM continues."

msgid "conglolem"
msgstr "Mouthguard Mo"

msgid "conifrost_description"
msgstr "If it sneezes, an avalanche occurs. It has a permanent sniffle."

msgid "conifrost"
msgstr "Open Mat Oz"

msgid "conileaf_description"
msgstr ""
"Foods placed in its pitcher are blended and pickled. They are used to store "
"food without it going off."

msgid "conileaf"
msgstr "Comp Class Cam"

msgid "coppi_description"
msgstr ""
"COPPI's flowers are surprisingly bitter and smelly, but they are useful in "
"beer brewing and medicine."

msgid "coppi"
msgstr "Stall Steve"

msgid "coproblight_description"
msgstr ""
"Born from the feces of prehistoric Tuxemon, it used the shards of bone "
"within itself for defense."

msgid "coproblight"
msgstr "Grippy Greg"

msgid "corvix_description"
msgstr "It arms its wings with bone shards from its victims."

msgid "corvix"
msgstr "Underhook Ugo"

msgid "cowpignon_description"
msgstr "Some people dry it out and eat it as a medicinal enhancement."

msgid "cowpignon"
msgstr "Overhook Owen"

msgid "crankus_description"
msgstr ""
"From one mountaintop to another, CRANKUS can be heard bleating to one "
"another in running arguments that end only with the spring thaws."

msgid "crankus"
msgstr "Backtake Baz"

msgid "criniotherme_description"
msgstr ""
"Its mane shines during the day, grows big and red at sunset, and blows away "
"as ash at night."

msgid "criniotherme"
msgstr "Snapdown Sid"

msgid "crustagu_description"
msgstr ""
"It fires piercing, poisonous spines from its claws to frighten away those "
"who threaten its underwater colonies."

msgid "crustagu"
msgstr "Ankle Pick Al"

msgid "dandicub_description"
msgstr ""
"After a litter is born, they float all over the world and never see their "
"family again."

msgid "dandicub"
msgstr "Collar Carl"

msgid "dandylion_description"
msgstr ""
"It gives birth to one litter in its life. Then it wanders the world trying "
"to find them."

msgid "dandylion"
msgstr "Lapel Larry"

msgid "dankush_description"
msgstr ""
"A DANKUSH can stop itself from burning by holding its breath, causing plumes"
" of smoke to billow forth from each leaf."

msgid "dankush"
msgstr "Knee Slice Kai"

msgid "delfeco_description"
msgstr ""
"DELFECO's streamlined body allows for swift navigation through water, and "
"its intelligence is evident in its complex hunting strategies. Despite its "
"size, it's known for its playful nature and strong bond with its trainer."

msgid "delfeco"
msgstr "Turtle Terry"

msgid "demosnow_description"
msgstr ""
"DEMOSNOW delight in luring travelers deeper into the wilderness than is "
"strictly safe, promising them glory and adventure."

msgid "demosnow"
msgstr "Shrimp Sean"

msgid "devidin_description"
msgstr ""
"A dicynodont that came back to life and decided to become the dinosaur "
"everyone always mistakes it for."

msgid "devidin"
msgstr "Bridge Barry"

msgid "devidra_description"
msgstr ""
"Look closely, for ultra fine fur gives away it is devilishly pretending to "
"be a dinosaur."

msgid "devidra"
msgstr "Mounty Mike"

msgid "deviraptor_description"
msgstr ""
"The single pair of feathers on its head are fakes, hinting at its devilish "
"true identity."

msgid "deviraptor"
msgstr "SideCtrl Sid"

msgid "dinoflop_description"
msgstr ""
"DINOFLOP delights in quickly turning away from its attackers so their blows "
"land on its shielded and spiny back."

msgid "dinoflop"
msgstr "Coach Big Ron"

msgid "djinnbo_description"
msgstr ""
"It is mistakenly believed that it is a human who died in a fire. Actually, "
"its relatives did."

msgid "djinnbo"
msgstr "Mum Said No"

msgid "doctsky_description"
msgstr ""
"The little hyena just wants to take care of others, but has a bad reputation"
" after a movie with it as a villain came out."

msgid "doctsky"
msgstr "Mat Karen"

msgid "dollfin_description"
msgstr "Each one follows a ship from place to place, exploring the world."

msgid "dollfin"
msgstr "Drama Dan"

msgid "dracune_description"
msgstr "It is immobile during the day, but can wriggle and bite at night."

msgid "dracune"
msgstr "Daisy NoGi"

msgid "dragarbor_description"
msgstr ""
"When it feels it is coming to the end of its life, it travels to a graveyard"
" where it plants itself. Its tail flower grows forever."

msgid "dragarbor"
msgstr "Sweaty Betty"

msgid "drashimi_description"
msgstr ""
"It lies on the ground, smelling delicious and tempting monsters to take a "
"bite - but when they approach, it bites them first."

msgid "drashimi"
msgstr "Bonk Barry"

msgid "drokoro_description"
msgstr ""
"Once it had a family, but it ate its parents, and it ate its children, and "
"it ate its mate, and it ate all of its kind."

msgid "drokoro"
msgstr "Shady Shane"

msgid "duggot_description"
msgstr ""
"When TUMBLEBEE tries to drink fruit juice, a DUGGOT may latch on and take "
"over its brain."

msgid "duggot"
msgstr "Creepy Craig"

msgid "dune_pincher_description"
msgstr ""
"These hermits will wrap themselves in whatever is closest. In the desert, "
"that is the burial shrouds of long-dead pharaohs."

msgid "dune_pincher"
msgstr "Moody Molly"

msgid "eaglace_description"
msgstr ""
"When it takes flight, clouds form. When it claps its wings, hail falls."

msgid "eaglace"
msgstr "Nasty Nancy"

msgid "elofly_description"
msgstr ""
"An ELOFLY on its own is patient and wise, but when it flocks in great "
"numbers it becomes violent and impulsive."

msgid "elofly"
msgstr "Porrada Pam"

msgid "elostorm_description"
msgstr ""
"Kings and queens, the ELOSTORM rule their people and have great ambition."

msgid "elostorm"
msgstr "Kimura Kim"

msgid "elowind_description"
msgstr ""
"The lieutenants of the ELOFLY family, ELOWIND shepherd the flock and keep it"
" focused."

msgid "elowind"
msgstr "Heelhook Holly"

msgid "embazook_description"
msgstr "It is trained for use in war and it knows no other life."

msgid "embazook"
msgstr "Darce Debbie"

msgid "embra_description"
msgstr "It eats everything it can to grow big enough to become a RUPTION."

msgid "embra"
msgstr "Guillo Gina"

msgid "enduros_description"
msgstr ""
"ENDUROS is an aggressive brawler that does not pull its blows. Out of the "
"ring, it is quite sociable."

msgid "enduros"
msgstr "Acai Amy"

msgid "equill_description"
msgstr ""
"Its bitterness causes it to transform. It hides its ugliness in the dark."

msgid "equill"
msgstr "NoGi Nora"

msgid "eruptibus_description"
msgstr "Smiths work with it, heating up metals in its caldera."

msgid "eruptibus"
msgstr "Judo Jenny"

msgid "erythroskyte_description"
msgstr ""
"It has a friendly demeanor, but its giant syringe tail nonetheless scares "
"many away."

msgid "erythroskyte"
msgstr "Spazzy Sally"

msgid "eskipup_description"
msgstr "Even as a puppy, it can pull 1 ton loads."

msgid "eskipup"
msgstr "Tappy Tammy"

msgid "exapode_description"
msgstr ""
"It waves its legs to attract attention, but mostly people just run away."

msgid "exapode"
msgstr "Guard Gina"

msgid "exclawvate_description"
msgstr ""
"Often seen on construction sites, they can use their huge hands and tail to "
"scoop up dirt and rubble. Underneath the Tuxemon are caterpillar tires, "
"giving them a better balance and grip while climbing heaps of rubble."

msgid "exclawvate"
msgstr "Mount Mandy"

msgid "eyenemy_description"
msgstr "It feeds on beautiful views and other spectacular sights."

msgid "eyenemy"
msgstr "Triangle Tina"

msgid "eyesore_description"
msgstr ""
"It remembers everything it has ever seen, but not the order that it has seen"
" it in."

msgid "eyesore"
msgstr "Bonnie BlueBelt"

msgid "fancair_description"
msgstr ""
"If someone leaves their fan running when they do not need it, it comes alive"
" and flies out the window to find someone who actually needs to be cooled."

msgid "fancair"
msgstr "Slutty Sarah"

msgid "ferricran_description"
msgstr ""
"Once, the FERRICRAN were covered all over with adamantine scales, and had "
"wings of mithril."

msgid "ferricran"
msgstr "Only Dans"

msgid "firomenis_description"
msgstr ""
"These tuxemon are large and tough from the many years spent as a MERLICUN. "
"Their jaws can crush through trees and bones, and their flight is strong "
"enough to carry people."

msgid "firomenis"
msgstr "Mat Bastard"

msgid "flacono_description"
msgstr ""
"It is totally unafraid of adversaries, and will attack an enemy of any size "
"without hesitation."

msgid "flacono"
msgstr "Gi Goblin"

msgid "flambear_description"
msgstr ""
"It can be tracked from the trail of boiled berry bushes and roasted trout it"
" leaves in its wake."

msgid "flambear"
msgstr "Heelhook Harry"

msgid "flisces_description"
msgstr ""
"It skims the surface of the water, evading detection until a powerful leap "
"brings its sharp fins into play."

msgid "flisces"
msgstr "Dr Kimura"

msgid "fluoresfin_description"
msgstr ""
"When threatened, it huddles together with other FLUORESFIN to create a large"
" blinding light to disorientate predators."

msgid "fluoresfin"
msgstr "Craig NoGi"

msgid "fluttaflap_description"
msgstr ""
"It feeds on impurities, so it returns purified blood to those it sucks on."

msgid "fluttaflap"
msgstr "Wristlock Wes"

msgid "foofle_description"
msgstr "When one is in danger, all FOOFLE hear its cries, wherever they are."

msgid "foofle"
msgstr "Stinky Gi"

msgid "flounce_description"
msgstr ""
"FLOUNCE can be stubborn and solitary, flouncing all the rules unless given "
"good motivation."

msgid "flounce"
msgstr "Coach Atlas"

msgid "flummack_description"
msgstr ""
"FLUMMACK no longer desires to be eaten, but to eat - even other FLUMMBY and "
"FLUMMACK go down a treat."

msgid "flummack"
msgstr "Spazzy Steve"

msgid "flummby_description"
msgstr ""
"FLUMMBY was invented by a scientist who thought food that wanted to be eaten"
" would be more ethical. It leaps into the mouth of anyone who could eat it."

msgid "flummby"
msgstr "Acai Slut"

msgid "fordin_description"
msgstr "When threatened, it curls into a ball and bounces away."

msgid "fordin"
msgstr "Nasty Nate"

msgid "forturtle_description"
msgstr "It heats its shell to read the future from the cracks that emerge."

msgid "forturtle"
msgstr "Oilcheck Oz"

msgid "foxfire_description"
msgstr ""
"FOXFIRE cubs are found in fires that burned out overnight. No one knows "
"where they come from."

msgid "foxfire"
msgstr "Leglock Larry"

msgid "fribbit_description"
msgstr "It is said that it was once a boy who licked a freezing lamp post."

msgid "fribbit"
msgstr "Sandbag Sam"

msgid "frondly_description"
msgstr ""
"It can do anything with its prehensile tail, even shake hands and pick "
"fruit."

msgid "frondly"
msgstr "Sweaty Kev"

msgid "frostuce_description"
msgstr "One rarely expects to see green waltzing around in a snowstorm."

msgid "frostuce"
msgstr "Choke Chad"

msgid "fruitera_description"
msgstr ""
"FRUITERA is greedy for fruit, and carries as much as it can. When startled, "
"it drops all its fruit, gathers it all up again, and only then runs away."

msgid "fruitera"
msgstr "Tapout Tim"

msgid "furnursus_description"
msgstr ""
"FURNURSUS are friendly, and often forget that their bodies are too hot for "
"others to touch."

msgid "furnursus"
msgstr "Guard Slag"

msgid "fuzzina_description"
msgstr ""
"When the child that abandoned a FUZZLET needs it again, it becomes a "
"FUZZINA, a brave protector and nurturer of the small and the weak."

msgid "fuzzina"
msgstr "Kimura Kev"

msgid "fuzzlet_description"
msgstr ""
"When a child is no longer around to play with their toys, they sometimes "
"come to life."

msgid "fuzzlet"
msgstr "Mount Mick"

msgid "galasces_description"
msgstr "GALASCES can distort its shape to engulf prey its own size."

msgid "galasces"
msgstr "Halfguard Hal"

msgid "galnec_description"
msgstr ""
"GALNEC buries itself deep in the hot sands of the desert, only its stony "
"tail above ground. In packs, they look like gardens of stone."

msgid "galnec"
msgstr "Judo Jake"

msgid "gastronium_description"
msgstr ""
"GASTRONIUM can eat almost anything but prefers heavy, radioactive materials."

msgid "gastronium"
msgstr "Wrestle Dad"

msgid "gectile_description"
msgstr "It is so quick and light that it can walk on leaves."

msgid "gectile"
msgstr "Neck Crank Ned"

msgid "ghosteeth_description"
msgstr "It smiles because it knows how everyone it meets is going to die."

msgid "ghosteeth"
msgstr "Buggy Ben"

msgid "dynastor_description"
msgstr ""
"DYNASTOR is a massive insectoid tuxemon with a deep, armored exoskeleton"
" and distinctive wings running along its back. Its mandibles can crush "
"steel. "

msgid "dynastor"
msgstr "Rough Rachel"

msgid "gliffary_description"
msgstr ""
"A mischievous fey creature that is rarely seen, it gathers by mushroom rings"
" and melts iron zealously."

msgid "gliffary"
msgstr "Degen Dan"

msgid "glombroc_description"
msgstr ""
"It stores its memories in its rocky shell. If some fall off, it is "
"forgetful."

msgid "glombroc"
msgstr "Mat Rat"

msgid "glomon_description"
msgstr ""
"A colony of bacteria that became new life in a discarded medical glove. It "
"can see out of the back of its body."

msgid "glomon"
msgstr "Bluebelt Ben"

msgid "golnagi_description"
msgstr ""
"GOLNAGI's scales glow, making it almost invisible in the water during dawn "
"and dusk - its preferred times for hunting."

msgid "golnagi"
msgstr "Purple Paul"

msgid "gourda_description"
msgstr ""
"Competitions to grow the largest GOURDA have resulted in some reaching one "
"ton in weight, but normal GOURDA are much smaller."

msgid "gourda"
msgstr "Brownbelt Bert"

msgid "graffiki_description"
msgstr ""
"GRAFFIKI are as at home in cities as they are in the jungle, tagging their "
"territory with elaborate paintings."

msgid "graffiki"
msgstr "Blackbelt Baz"

msgid "grimachin_description"
msgstr "It was made by a toy company to be a pet, but was too dangerous."

msgid "grimachin"
msgstr "Fake Coach"

msgid "grinflare_description"
msgstr "It is said that each is the walking heart of a volcano."

msgid "grinflare"
msgstr "Trial Tony"

msgid "grintot_description"
msgstr "It is a GRINTROCK or GRINFLARE that has experienced erosion."

msgid "grintot"
msgstr "Creonte Carl"

msgid "grintrock_description"
msgstr ""
"It feeds by sitting out in thunderstorms, waiting to be struck by lightning."

msgid "grintrock"
msgstr "Manky Mike"

msgid "grumpi_description"
msgstr ""
"Once grabbed by a GRUMPI, its sticky tacky body is impossible to escape "
"from."

msgid "grumpi"
msgstr "Spicy Steve"

msgid "gryfix_description"
msgstr "Bone armor protects GRYFIX from all but the most powerful of attacks."

msgid "gryfix"
msgstr "Gassy Gaz"

msgid "gupphire_description"
msgstr ""
"GUPPHIRE's scales sparkle, making it a stunning sight to behold. Fishers who"
" see a GUPPHIRE believe it means they will have good luck all year."

msgid "gupphire"
msgstr "Toehold Tom"

msgid "gupphish_description"
msgstr ""
"GUPPHISH loves to swim in schools, making it a popular choice for trainers "
"who value teamwork."

msgid "gupphish"
msgstr "RNC Ray"

msgid "hampotamos_description"
msgstr "It nibbles on RINOCEREED, clearing away dead skin, moss and weeds."

msgid "hampotamos"
msgstr "Smash Pass Sam"

msgid "happito_description"
msgstr ""
"Why can't people always be happy? HAPPITO will give them exactly what they "
"want, even if it is not what they need."

msgid "happito"
msgstr "Juice Josh"

msgid "hatchling_description"
msgstr ""
"When an egg does not want to hatch and begin its next life stage, it becomes"
" a HATCHLING."

msgid "hatchling"
msgstr "Cringe Craig"

msgid "hectapod_description"
msgstr ""
"When it inflates its dome, it floats to the top of oceans, or even through "
"mist and clouds."

msgid "hectapod"
msgstr "Lazy Larry"

msgid "helipi_description"
msgstr ""
"It flies farther with one wing by rotating than with two, but sacrifices the"
" ability to easily aim."

msgid "helipi"
msgstr "Dojo Derek"

msgid "heronquak_description"
msgstr ""
"The crystal on its chest is mistaken for a diamond by poachers. It melts "
"when it is removed from HERONQUAK's body."

msgid "heronquak"
msgstr "Shark Tank Sam"

msgid "hissiorite_description"
msgstr ""
"The base of its neck emits super-heated gas that envelopes its body and "
"causes it to hover a few inches off the ground, similar to a hot air "
"balloon. Because of this it can travel quickly, even over water."

msgid "hissiorite"
msgstr "Nosebeer Neil"

msgid "hoarse_description"
msgstr "It appears to be a farm animal, but it was mistreated by its owner."

msgid "hoarse"
msgstr "Kneeride Kev"

msgid "hoarseshoo_description"
msgstr "It is what is left when an EQUILL's shadow eats its body."

msgid "hoarseshoo"
msgstr "Pullguard Pat"

msgid "hoodoll_description"
msgstr ""
"It sometimes sticks a pin in itself to curse its foes, but no one can tell "
"the difference after."

msgid "hoodoll"
msgstr "Dirty Dan"

msgid "hotline_description"
msgstr ""
"These curious creatures can leap great distances, letting out a strange, "
"tinny cry that cannot be escaped however far their prey runs."

msgid "hotline"
msgstr "Tap Daddy"

msgid "houndice_description"
msgstr ""
"HOUNDICE loves sledding, but it can also sniff out lost hikers under snow."

msgid "houndice"
msgstr "Gym Thot"

msgid "howl_description"
msgstr ""
"HOWL's foolish exterior hides deep wisdom - if only it could communicate it,"
" but its words come out as hoots and howls."

msgid "howl"
msgstr "Acai Addict"

msgid "hydrone_description"
msgstr "It utilizes an experimental technology that creates power from water."

msgid "hydrone"
msgstr "Blue Belt Ex"

msgid "ignibus_description"
msgstr ""
"When threatened it retreats into its shell and cools down dramatically by "
"venting steam. It could be mistaken for a rock."

msgid "ignibus"
msgstr "Guard Goblin"

msgid "imbrickcile_description"
msgstr ""
"IMBRICKCILE shelter inside a single brick, emerging only to lift it to build"
" their strength."

msgid "imbrickcile"
msgstr "Leglock Luke"

msgid "incandesfin_description"
msgstr ""
"Its entire body has massively grown in size. However, its light is still the"
" exact same."

msgid "incandesfin"
msgstr "Wristlock Will"

msgid "jelillow_description"
msgstr ""
"When a person rests their head on JELILLOW, its jelly-like skin causes them "
"to fall into a deep sleep. If someone is having sleeping problems, then this"
" monster will be used to help them."

msgid "jelillow"
msgstr "Mat Enforcer"

msgid "jeluna_description"
msgstr ""
"The moon exercises its strange influence on Jeluna, causing these aerial "
"jellyfish to change their forms over the course of a month."

msgid "jeluna"
msgstr "Purple Perve"

msgid "jemuar_description"
msgstr ""
"The gems on its back are the type found when it was born. There are "
"extensive ROCKITTEN breeding facilities over diamond veins."

msgid "jemuar"
msgstr "Coach Creepy"

msgid "joulraton_description"
msgstr ""
"Its static coat of bristly fur attracts seeds, flowers and feathers, which "
"it uses for food or nesting materials."

msgid "joulraton"
msgstr "NoGi Niall"

msgid "k9_description"
msgstr "It is a helpful companion that can pull a tonne of weight."

msgid "k9"
msgstr "Trial Guy"

msgid "katacoon_description"
msgstr ""
"It stays in a meditative pose for its chrysalis, moving only to jab enemies."

msgid "katacoon"
msgstr "Whitebelt Will"

msgid "katapill_description"
msgstr ""
"It is born fighting. It has to punch out of its eggshell or be trapped."

msgid "katapill"
msgstr "Brownbelt Ben"

msgid "kernel_description"
msgstr ""
"KERNEL is a core component of the monster system (kennel) and item system "
"(locker), and serves as the main interface between the computer's physical "
"hardware and the processes running on it. Known as JAS-KERI-BIT from its "
"creators."

msgid "kernel"
msgstr "Blackbelt Bob"

msgid "knightsand_description"
msgstr ""
"KNIGHTSAND patrols around sand castles inhabits by PAWSAND, but is terrible "
"at building them."

msgid "knightsand"
msgstr "Darce Dave"

msgid "knindling_description"
msgstr "Any spark from a stone KNINDLING happily tenders into a fire."

msgid "knindling"
msgstr "Guillo Gary"

msgid "komodraw_description"
msgstr ""
"It uses its claws to carve its firearm out of wood, and uses it for powerful"
" ranged attacks."

msgid "komodraw"
msgstr "Armbar Andy"

msgid "komoduel_description"
msgstr ""
"Many a wrongdoer has fled town after seeing just the silhouette of an "
"approaching KOMODUEL."

msgid "komoduel"
msgstr "Triangle Tom"

msgid "konuit_description"
msgstr ""
"In some places KONUIT is called 'drop bear' and believed to fall on "
"unsuspecting heads below."

msgid "konuit"
msgstr "Berimbolo Ben"

msgid "kroki_description"
msgstr ""
"KROKI spends most of its time in shallow waters, using its powerful jaws to "
"snap at prey."

msgid "kroki"
msgstr "Kesa Ken"

msgid "krokivip_description"
msgstr ""
"This venomous crocodilian enjoys ambushing from the water. As it grows "
"closer to evolution, it seeks out larger bodies of water."

msgid "krokivip"
msgstr "Sambo Sam"

msgid "lambert_description"
msgstr ""
"It is placed in its nut by its parent, who then sends it into the world."

msgid "lambert"
msgstr "Panic Pete"

msgid "lapinou_description"
msgstr ""
"When SQUABBITS were taken as fashionable pets, they adapted to domestic life"
" and lost their violent natures."

msgid "lapinou"
msgstr "Sweat Goblin"

msgid "legko_description"
msgstr "Long thought to be legless, its leaves are actually vestigial limbs."

msgid "legko"
msgstr "Tape Finger"

msgid "legoplaste_description"
msgstr ""
"It has a very fluid shape and may hunt by sending out random tendrils to "
"sniff or touch nearby prey."

msgid "legoplaste"
msgstr "Cauli Carl"

msgid "lendos_description"
msgstr "When two UNEYE become tangled, they form a single unified LENDOS."

msgid "lendos"
msgstr "Shit Gi Sean"

msgid "lesmagu_description"
msgstr ""
"It oozes along the sea floor, looking for hard nooks and crannies to hide in"
" until it develops its shell."

msgid "lesmagu"
msgstr "Toe Hold Ted"

msgid "lettice_description"
msgstr "Cold weather concentrates the power and vitality of LETTICE."

msgid "lettice"
msgstr "Mouthguard Mo"

msgid "leviadile_description"
msgstr ""
"With its immense size and powerful venomous jaws, LEVIADILE is a dominant "
"predator of the deep sea."

msgid "leviadile"
msgstr "Open Mat Oz"

msgid "lightmare_description"
msgstr ""
"It lurks in the depths of the ocean, luring any unsuspecting prey using its "
"light right into its large, gaping mouth."

msgid "lightmare"
msgstr "Comp Class Cam"

msgid "loliferno_description"
msgstr ""
"It is said that the LOLIFERNO's fire could not be extinguished. Yet, despite"
" its power, LOLIFERNO has a playful side, and is known to dance among the "
"flames it creates."

msgid "loliferno"
msgstr "Stall Steve"

msgid "lucifice_description"
msgstr ""
"Is it the wind howling through the trees, or LUCIFICE calling the dark "
"spirits of the night to join its hunt?"

msgid "lucifice"
msgstr "Grippy Greg"

msgid "lunight_description"
msgstr ""
"LUNIGHT is the guardian of the night, and can control the moon and its "
"phases."

msgid "lunight"
msgstr "Underhook Ugo"

msgid "magmaturtle_description"
msgstr ""
"When threatened it retreats into its shell and cools down dramatically by "
"venting steam. It could be mistaken for a rock."

msgid "magmaturtle"
msgstr "Magmaturtle"

msgid "manosting_description"
msgstr "It floats across the tops of cities, contemplating sharks."

msgid "manosting"
msgstr "Overhook Owen"

msgid "marvantis_description"
msgstr ""
"When it evolves, the only trace of its original mimicry is its red "
"ornaments."

msgid "marvantis"
msgstr "Backtake Baz"

msgid "marvillar_description"
msgstr ""
"MARVILLAR mimes an ant larva using scent. It convinces SCARLANT and "
"MYRMISON to feed it, eating skeptics."

msgid "marvillar"
msgstr "Snapdown Sid"

msgid "masknake_description"
msgstr ""
"When frightened or aggressive, it flashes a beautiful pattern with its tail."

msgid "masknake"
msgstr "Ankle Pick Al"

msgid "mauai_description"
msgstr ""
"MAUAI gives itself over to the spirits of lost warriors trapped inside its "
"weapon."

msgid "mauai"
msgstr "Blast Dan"

msgid "medipup_description"
msgstr ""
"When MEDIPUP sniff out sickness, they bounce over and nuzzle the affected "
"creature. MEDIPUP's wet noses are effective, but some patients have been "
"crushed under an overly enthusiastic pack."

msgid "medipup"
msgstr "Collar Carl"

msgid "medushock_description"
msgstr ""
"Tend to stay away from shore and known to be aggressive to people. Stingers "
"are used to stun its prey. Swim safely."

msgid "medushock"
msgstr "Lapel Larry"

msgid "megafruitera_description"
msgstr ""
"It has slightly better self control than its younger form, enlarging its "
"nest first if it needs to for extra fruit."

msgid "megafruitera"
msgstr "Knee Slice Kai"

msgid "memnomnom_description"
msgstr "It is said that each one's mask is the face of a different dead king."

msgid "memnomnom"
msgstr "Pressure Pat"

msgid "merlicun_description"
msgstr ""
"Merlicun is a hardy insect that has evolved to be efficient at both attack "
"and defense. They gather in the tree canopies of ancient forests to feed on "
"fruits and leaves."

msgid "merlicun"
msgstr "Turtle Terry"

msgid "metesaur_description"
msgstr ""
"This Tuxemon would enjoy diving into the ground and leaving marks. "
"Sometimes, the Tuxemon would misjudge the hit and land in trees, starting "
"huge and dangerous forest fires."

msgid "metesaur"
msgstr "Shrimp Sean"

msgid "metoxic_description"
msgstr ""
"METOXIC sometimes acts as a flag for PAWSAND castles, spewing poisonous "
"fumes everywhere."

msgid "metoxic"
msgstr "Bridge Barry"

msgid "miaownolith_description"
msgstr "It can speak the human tongue, but only to say cryptic riddles."

msgid "miaownolith"
msgstr "Mounty Mike"

msgid "mingdyn_description"
msgstr ""
"Every 12 years, a single MINGDYN egg is laid. Its discovery marks a time of "
"renewal and upheaval across the land."

msgid "mingdyn"
msgstr "SideCtrl Sid"

msgid "moloch_description"
msgstr "It can stiffen or soften its skin to respond to friends and foes."

msgid "moloch"
msgstr "Bonk Barry"

msgid "mrmoswitch_description"
msgstr ""
"These cheeky robots are used for their fine motor skills, but they love "
"pranks."

msgid "mrmoswitch"
msgstr "Shady Shane"

msgid "myrmison_description"
msgstr ""
"MYRMISON queens will emerge on humid days to try to establish new colonies. "
"This is a very dangerous time for them."

msgid "myrmison"
msgstr "Creepy Craig"

msgid "mystikapi_description"
msgstr ""
"The MYSTIKAPI's saliva augments psychic powers. It licks its eyes and ears "
"to heighten its senses."

msgid "mystikapi"
msgstr "Moody Molly"

msgid "narcileaf_description"
msgstr ""
"When a SHYBULB has restored a garden to glory, it morphs and proudly takes "
"credit for its work."

msgid "narcileaf"
msgstr "Rough Rachel"

msgid "nebufin_description"
msgstr ""
"NEBUFIN's angelic appearance is deceptive, as the monster is predatory."

msgid "nebufin"
msgstr "Nasty Nancy"

msgid "ned_description"
msgstr ""
"NED has a rivalry with KONUIT, but KONUIT sleeps through most of their "
"arguments."

msgid "ned"
msgstr "Porrada Pam"

msgid "neutrito_description"
msgstr "NEUTRITO feels nothing. The perfect machine?"

msgid "neutrito"
msgstr "Kimura Kim"

msgid "nimbulex_description"
msgstr ""
"NIMBULEX dresses itself in sparks and storm clouds to protect its delicate "
"inner core."

msgid "nimbulex"
msgstr "Heelhook Holly"

msgid "ninjasmine_description"
msgstr "NINJASMINE poisons his opponents quickly using his two poison swords."

msgid "ninjasmine"
msgstr "Darce Debbie"

msgid "noctalo_description"
msgstr ""
"It inhabits only places abandoned by humans - castles, graveyards and "
"sewers."

msgid "noctalo"
msgstr "Guillo Gina"

msgid "noctula_description"
msgstr ""
"It eats fruit and PIPIS eat bugs, so despite living in close proximity they "
"do not compete."

msgid "noctula"
msgstr "Acai Amy"

msgid "nostray_description"
msgstr "It can smell anything in the ocean, no matter how far away."

msgid "nostray"
msgstr "NoGi Nora"

msgid "novaquarius_description"
msgstr ""
"A NOVAQUARIUS sting sends the unwary to the hospital, but BUBBITOISE have "
"developed immunity and will nibble on them."

msgid "novaquarius"
msgstr "Judo Jenny"

msgid "nudiflot_female_description"
msgstr ""
"It eats and stores the poison of the sea creatures that it feeds upon."

msgid "nudiflot_female"
msgstr "Spazzy Sally"

msgid "nudiflot_male_description"
msgstr ""
"Its feathery antennas snap off if it is attacked, confusing the predator."

msgid "nudiflot_male"
msgstr "Tappy Tammy"

msgid "nudikill_description"
msgstr ""
"They are called Dark Bishops because their heads are reminiscent of a "
"bishop's hat."

msgid "nudikill"
msgstr "Guard Gina"

msgid "nudimind_description"
msgstr "It dreams of oceans under other skies."

msgid "nudimind"
msgstr "Mount Mandy"

msgid "nuenflu_description"
msgstr "It snuggles in homes in the winter months, spreading diseases."

msgid "nuenflu"
msgstr "Triangle Tina"

msgid "nut_description"
msgstr ""
"In the great ships that cross the oceans, thousands of NUT and BOLT provide "
"power and hold the steel plating together."

msgid "nut"
msgstr "Bonnie BlueBelt"

msgid "octabode_description"
msgstr ""
"OCTABODE make ancient vessels and artifacts their homes, dreaming of the "
"lives of those who used the relics before them."

msgid "octabode"
msgstr "Vegan Niall"

msgid "ouroboutlet_description"
msgstr ""
"The circuit focuses energy, creating a new type of electricity called "
"griefed-lightning."

msgid "ouroboutlet"
msgstr "Slutty Sarah"

msgid "pairagrim_description"
msgstr ""
"One of PAIRAGRIM's heads is always searching for prey, while the other "
"focuses on flying at great speed."

msgid "pairagrim"
msgstr "Only Dans"

msgid "pairagrin_description"
msgstr ""
"The young form of Pairagrim, it is a generally happy creature. It struggles "
"to fly until the two heads learn to work together."

msgid "pairagrin"
msgstr "Mat Bastard"

msgid "pantherafira_description"
msgstr ""
"Each member of the pride lights their mane from a shared bonfire. As long as"
" that fire burns, their strength is shared."

msgid "pantherafira"
msgstr "Gi Goblin"

msgid "parappi_description"
msgstr ""
"When cut PARAPPI oozes syrup that seals and hardens over its enemies, "
"turning them to amber."

msgid "parappi"
msgstr "Heelhook Harry"

msgid "pawsand_description"
msgstr ""
"PAWSAND inhabits sand castles and sand temples made by BISHOSAND and "
"ROOKSAND, some of which are actually ROOKSAND itself."

msgid "pawsand"
msgstr "Dr Kimura"

msgid "pearamanca_description"
msgstr ""
"PEARAMANCA sells insurance to innocent people just trying to buy fruit, "
"which makes it the most terrifying monster of all."

msgid "pearamanca"
msgstr "Coach Atlas"

msgid "pharavion_description"
msgstr ""
"After great effort, a trainer may evolve a clumsy PHARFAN calf into its "
"adult form, which gracefully floats despite its huge size."

msgid "pharavion"
msgstr "Spazzy Steve"

msgid "pharfan_description"
msgstr ""
"At the watering hole it keeps its friends RINOCEREED and HAMPOTAMOS well "
"watered."

msgid "pharfan"
msgstr "Acai Slut"

msgid "picc_description"
msgstr "It accompanies divers, providing much needed oxygen."

msgid "picc"
msgstr "Craig NoGi"

msgid "pickoon_description"
msgstr ""
"It enjoys picking things up and stuffing them discreetly into its scarf."

msgid "pickoon"
msgstr "Wristlock Wes"

msgid "pigabyte_description"
msgstr "Scientists found that the best computers have organic implants."

msgid "pigabyte"
msgstr "Stinky Gi"

msgid "pilthropus_description"
msgstr ""
"Found alongside Tuxemon such as RHINCUS, PILTHROPUS was one of the oldest "
"Tuxemon able to create its own tools."

msgid "pilthropus"
msgstr "Nasty Nate"

msgid "pipis_description"
msgstr "Its cries are considered a bad omen, but it is a gentle creature."

msgid "pipis"
msgstr "Oilcheck Oz"

msgid "poinchin_description"
msgstr ""
"POINCHIN make nests in the coral and can be tempted out by bread and milk."

msgid "poinchin"
msgstr "Leglock Larry"

msgid "polyrock_description"
msgstr ""
"It disguises itself as a human child to sneak into dojos and learn from "
"martial arts masters."

msgid "polyrock"
msgstr "Porrada Paul"

msgid "possessun_description"
msgstr "It is a ghost that inhabits a dead CAIRFREY."

msgid "possessun"
msgstr "Sandbag Sam"

msgid "potturmeist_description"
msgstr ""
"POTTURMEIST are spirits of the dead that take refuge in empty vessels. In "
"ancient temples, acolytes must distract the monsters lest they interrupt "
"important ceremonies."

msgid "potturmeist"
msgstr "Sweaty Kev"

msgid "potturney_description"
msgstr ""
"By the time a POTTURMEIST has reached its maturity, its protective urn has "
"so changed shape that it resembles no pottery made by human hands. Some "
"insist that the designs on a POTTURMEIST's urn are writings from the far "
"future."

msgid "potturney"
msgstr "Choke Chad"

msgid "primordia_description"
msgstr "It is rumored to be the ancestor of all tuxemon."

msgid "primordia"
msgstr "Tapout Tim"

msgid "propellercat_description"
msgstr "Is it a new species, or just the pet of an inventor?"

msgid "propellercat"
msgstr "Guard Slag"

msgid "prophetoise_description"
msgstr "Its heavenly fire is something foes rarely see coming."

msgid "prophetoise"
msgstr "Kimura Kev"

msgid "puparmor_description"
msgstr ""
"Its cocoon is so hard, people are knocked out if a PUPARMOR is dropped on "
"them. They were once loaded into cannons and catapults."

msgid "puparmor"
msgstr "Mount Mick"

msgid "pyraminx_description"
msgstr ""
"It has a tomb hidden somewhere in the land. If it finds it, it can sleep."

msgid "pyraminx"
msgstr "Halfguard Hal"

msgid "pythock_description"
msgstr ""
"Using its shadow puppets, it can use them to fight its opponent with great "
"accuracy and speed. They are much more confident, and will sometimes even "
"use their shadow puppets to entertain small children at puppet shows."

msgid "pythock"
msgstr "Judo Jake"

msgid "pythonova_description"
msgstr ""
"It is short tempered and when enraged, the flames on its back burn hotter "
"and its smoke tail becomes thicker and longer. It uses its smoke tail to "
"coil around and smother its target."

msgid "pythonova"
msgstr "Wrestle Dad"

msgid "pythwire_description"
msgstr ""
"Observations of wild PYTHWIRE inspired the inventor of the first electrical "
"outlet."

msgid "pythwire"
msgstr "Neck Crank Ned"

msgid "qetzlrokilus_description"
msgstr ""
"This Tuxemon would dive into groups of other dinosaur Tuxemon and burn them."
" They also enjoy setting forests alight and dropping their ashes into water "
"to spoil its purity."

msgid "qetzlrokilus"
msgstr "Buggy Ben"

msgid "rabbitosaur_description"
msgstr ""
"Its tunnels are extensive and wide, the site of tremendous wars between "
"burrows."

msgid "rabbitosaur"
msgstr "Mat Rat"

msgid "raccscal_description"
msgstr ""
"It has a baglike tail on its back that it can open and close, and even "
"detach and throw at enemies."

msgid "raccscal"
msgstr "Bluebelt Ben"

msgid "raptoucan_description"
msgstr "It is formidable and aggressive, but only eats fruit."

msgid "raptoucan"
msgstr "Purple Paul"

msgid "regalance_description"
msgstr "It can summon a halberd whenever it needs."

msgid "regalance"
msgstr "Brownbelt Bert"

msgid "rhincus_description"
msgstr "It has some properties of a reptile and some of a bird."

msgid "rhincus"
msgstr "Blackbelt Baz"

msgid "rhinocarpe_description"
msgstr ""
"RHINOCARPE are territorial, charging headfirst at any who swim too near to "
"their coral fortresses."

msgid "rhinocarpe"
msgstr "Fake Coach"

msgid "rinocereed_description"
msgstr ""
"It is voraciously hungry because it grows so quickly - and it does not limit"
" itself to plants."

msgid "rinocereed"
msgstr "Trial Tony"

msgid "rockat_description"
msgstr "Despite its considerable weight, its footfalls are silent."

msgid "rockat"
msgstr "Creonte Carl"

msgid "rockitten_description"
msgstr "It uses its tiny rock ears for snuggling."

msgid "rockitten"
msgstr "Manky Mike"

msgid "rooksand_description"
msgstr ""
"ROOKSAND sometimes allows those it deems worthy to live inside its "
"sandcastle, and crushes all others."

msgid "rooksand"
msgstr "Gassy Gaz"

msgid "rosarin_description"
msgstr "ROSARIN's love is incredible, he's only asking some affection."

msgid "rosarin"
msgstr "Toehold Tom"

msgid "ruffalo_description"
msgstr ""
"RUFFALO possess incredible strength and can charge at high speeds, capable "
"of knocking over trees and small buildings."

msgid "ruffalo"
msgstr "RNC Ray"

msgid "runesquito_description"
msgstr ""
"The blood-red marking is RUNESQUITO. The rest is just a rocky shell it rides"
" alongside."

msgid "runesquito"
msgstr "Smash Pass Sam"

msgid "ruption_description"
msgstr ""
"Once EMBRA's flame becomes hot enough, it engulfs its entire body, "
"essentially replacing it in the process."

msgid "ruption"
msgstr "Juice Josh"

msgid "sadito_description"
msgstr ""
"When a person is feeling too sad, SADITO will carry that burden for them."

msgid "sadito"
msgstr "Cringe Craig"

msgid "sampsack_description"
msgstr ""
"A scientist wanted to separate his personalities, but he split his body."

msgid "sampsack"
msgstr "Lazy Larry"

msgid "sampsage_description"
msgstr ""
"A scientist took a drug that made him clever by day and violent by night."

msgid "sampsage"
msgstr "Dojo Derek"

msgid "sapragon_description"
msgstr ""
"In olden times, each element had a mighty dragon - but those creatures have "
"diminished and are rare in these days."

msgid "sapragon"
msgstr "Shark Tank Sam"

msgid "sapsnap_description"
msgstr "Its terrific anger is off putting, but it passes quickly."

msgid "sapsnap"
msgstr "Nosebeer Neil"

msgid "saurchin_description"
msgstr ""
"By night, SAURCHIN emerge from the coral reefs to hunt bigger prey on land."

msgid "saurchin"
msgstr "Kneeride Kev"

msgid "scarlant_description"
msgstr "Its worst enemy is MARVILLAR, which pretends to be its kin."

msgid "scarlant"
msgstr "Pullguard Pat"

msgid "sclairus_description"
msgstr ""
"When a crop is left unharvested - be it from laziness or disaster - its "
"scarecrow becomes a dark and living creature."

msgid "sclairus"
msgstr "Dirty Dan"

msgid "seirein_description"
msgstr ""
"It grows lonely in the swamps, so it burns brightly to draw travelers near "
"- but it is painfully shy and flits away when they approach."

msgid "seirein"
msgstr "Tap Daddy"

msgid "selket_description"
msgstr ""
"Lying in wait beneath the sand, they can feel their prey through the "
"vibrations of their footsteps."

msgid "selket"
msgstr "Gym Thot"

msgid "selmatek_description"
msgstr ""
"Kept by the ancient kings of the deserts, SELMATEK served as watchdogs, "
"hunting companions and - now - defenders against grave robbers."

msgid "selmatek"
msgstr "Acai Addict"

msgid "seraphice_description"
msgstr ""
"SERAPHICE can freeze in ice moments of great courage and joy, stored away in"
" deep vaults beneath the mountains for the days when humanity will need them"
" most."

msgid "seraphice"
msgstr "Blue Belt Ex"

msgid "shammer_description"
msgstr "In ancient times it hunted RHINCUS beneath ashen skies."

msgid "shammer"
msgstr "Guard Goblin"

msgid "sharpfin_description"
msgstr ""
"It is invisible in the water, being visible only when it leaps out of the "
"water to drag animals on the shore back into the deep."

msgid "sharpfin"
msgstr "Leglock Luke"

msgid "shelagu_description"
msgstr ""
"It wards off attackers by poisoning its spiky shell with goo spat from its "
"mouth."

msgid "shelagu"
msgstr "Wristlock Will"

msgid "sheye_description"
msgstr ""
"SHEYE are weighed down by heavy thoughts. Edgy trainers like them for their "
"sinister appearance and solemn demeanor."

msgid "sheye"
msgstr "Mat Enforcer"

msgid "shimmerain_description"
msgstr ""
"They say that when a rainbow appears over water, the SHIMMERAIN are "
"spawning."

msgid "shimmerain"
msgstr "Purple Perve"

msgid "shnark_description"
msgstr ""
"SHNARK wears its last meal's flesh as a disguise so it can get close to its "
"trusting prey."

msgid "shnark"
msgstr "Coach Creepy"

msgid "shrab_description"
msgstr ""
"When a SHEYE frees its mind from always contemplating serious thoughts, it "
"becomes a SHRAB, free in body to wander the world."

msgid "shrab"
msgstr "NoGi Niall"

msgid "shybulb_description"
msgstr ""
"When a garden is neglected, a SHYBULB moves in and quietly tends the droopy "
"plants."

msgid "shybulb"
msgstr "Whitebelt Will"

msgid "shull_description"
msgstr ""
"SHULL doesn't need to eat or move, but it still enjoys treats and "
"supplements from its favorite person, especially if it is regularly being "
"sent into battle."

msgid "shull"
msgstr "Trial Guy"

msgid "skwib_description"
msgstr ""
"The SKWIB contentedly floats through the ocean, examining potential shell-"
"homes. It has to fear for its life before it will finally make a choice."

msgid "skwib"
msgstr "Brownbelt Ben"

msgid "slichen_description"
msgstr ""
"It is a gel that sparked to life and begins making a body for itself of "
"stone and rock."

msgid "slichen"
msgstr "Blackbelt Bob"

msgid "sludgehog_description"
msgstr ""
"It lives in rubbish, and eats it too. Its spikes seem sharp, but it can "
"soften them at will."

msgid "sludgehog"
msgstr "Darce Dave"

msgid "snaki_description"
msgstr ""
"SNAKI is a snake that has learned to grow legs by examining the motion of "
"lizards and crocodiles."

msgid "snaki"
msgstr "Guillo Gary"

msgid "snarlon_description"
msgstr ""
"It does not fly, but its feet never touch the ground. The king of paradox."

msgid "snarlon"
msgstr "Armbar Andy"

msgid "snock_description"
msgstr ""
"The snake-like creature hides under the safety of its sock cover. If "
"startled, it will flail and lie very still on the ground to avoid attention."

msgid "snock"
msgstr "Triangle Tom"

msgid "snokari_description"
msgstr ""
"The two heads of SNOKARI each hold great wisdom, but they never agree."

msgid "snokari"
msgstr "Berimbolo Ben"

msgid "snowrilla_description"
msgstr "It delights in playing tag with skiers on desolate slopes."

msgid "snowrilla"
msgstr "Kesa Ken"

msgid "sockeserp_description"
msgstr ""
"An otherwise formidable enemy, SOCKESERP is easily dispatched if it gets "
"tangled up."

msgid "sockeserp"
msgstr "Sambo Sam"

msgid "solight_description"
msgstr ""
"A villainous team is plotting to use SOLIGHT to create a miniature sun in "
"order to create a new planet."

msgid "solight"
msgstr "Judo Judas"

msgid "spectera_description"
msgstr ""
"This leaf-winged bat is omnivorous, but prefers fruit. Both the male and "
"female look after young."

msgid "spectera"
msgstr "Panic Pete"

msgid "sphake_description"
msgstr ""
"SPHAKE is sometimes responsible for small earthquakes that inconveniently "
"vibrate books and cups off your shelves; it eats whatever falls down."

msgid "sphake"
msgstr "Sweat Goblin"

msgid "spighter_description"
msgstr ""
"It's not fair that something so good at sneaking up on people, can't be "
"snuck up on itself."

msgid "spighter"
msgstr "Tape Finger"

msgid "spirain_description"
msgstr ""
"If a SEIREIN's inner fire dims, its water spirit nature turns it into "
"SPIRAIN."

msgid "spirain"
msgstr "Cauli Carl"

msgid "spoilurm_description"
msgstr ""
"SPOILURM disguise themselves as apples, and wait in trees to eat the "
"unsuspecting."

msgid "spoilurm"
msgstr "Shit Gi Sean"

msgid "sprightly_description"
msgstr ""
"A timid plant, it pops its head aboveground to drink water and sunshine. "

msgid "sprightly"
msgstr "Toe Hold Ted"

msgid "sprorm_description"
msgstr "SPRORM is fed on by CARDINALE, which can melt it down."

msgid "sprorm"
msgstr "Mouthguard Mo"

msgid "spycozeus_description"
msgstr ""
"The whispered communications of the forest are given physical form in "
"SPYCOZEUS, which thinks like the trees."

msgid "spycozeus"
msgstr "Open Mat Oz"

msgid "squabbit_description"
msgstr ""
"To prove themselves, they will fight tooth and nail over even the smallest "
"thing."

msgid "squabbit"
msgstr "Comp Class Cam"

msgid "squink_description"
msgstr "It is named for the noise it makes when it is all out of ink."

msgid "squink"
msgstr "Stall Steve"

msgid "statursus_description"
msgstr ""
"STATURSUS has learned to channel its emotions into a single pure flame. The "
"mere sight of it sends others into a trance."

msgid "statursus"
msgstr "Grippy Greg"

msgid "stegofor_description"
msgstr ""
"When it comes time to morph, STEGOFOR migrates in great herds along ancient "
"paths, stripping all vegetation from plants growing along the way."

msgid "stegofor"
msgstr "Underhook Ugo"

msgid "stomic_description"
msgstr ""
"STOMIC is radioactive, but radiation resistant bacteria like GLOMON still "
"pose a threat to it."

msgid "stomic"
msgstr "Overhook Owen"

msgid "stonifly_description"
msgstr ""
"STONIFLY's sturdy, rock-hard exoskeleton is a natural armor, while its "
"translucent wings allow for swift flight."

msgid "stonifly"
msgstr "Backtake Baz"

msgid "strella_description"
msgstr "Its tails are lures to convince bugs to bite them and be trapped."

msgid "strella"
msgstr "Snapdown Sid"

msgid "sumchon_description"
msgstr ""
"It uses its weight to trip much larger enemies. It is as dense as a star."

msgid "sumchon"
msgstr "Ankle Pick Al"

msgid "sumobug"
msgstr "Sumobug"

msgid "sumobug_description"
msgstr ""
"It uses its weight to trip much larger enemies. It is as dense as a star."

msgid "tadcool_description"
msgstr "It croaks to warn people when they are walking near thin ice."

msgid "tadcool"
msgstr "Blast Dan"

msgid "tarpeur_description"
msgstr ""
"They rest and grow. They also grow and rest. Rarely, they rest without "
"growing or grow without resting."

msgid "tarpeur"
msgstr "Collar Carl"

msgid "taupypus_description"
msgstr ""
"Upon their birth, a TAUPYPUS' eyes are burst by its mother. That way, their "
"eyes will never sting when they dive into the water."

msgid "taupypus"
msgstr "Lapel Larry"

msgid "teddisun_description"
msgstr ""
"TEDDISUN worships the sun - they're always seen carrying their sun toy."

msgid "teddisun"
msgstr "Knee Slice Kai"

msgid "tetrchimp_description"
msgstr ""
"They absorb any information they come across. Their constant chatter "
"communicates everything they have learned in order."

msgid "tetrchimp"
msgstr "Pressure Pat"

msgid "thumpurn_description"
msgstr ""
"They thump their enemies with their fists, and thump the ground to give "
"warnings."

msgid "thumpurn"
msgstr "Turtle Terry"

msgid "tigrock_description"
msgstr ""
"It is said that it had to invent itself because an evolution was not "
"designed."

msgid "tigrock"
msgstr "Shrimp Sean"

msgid "tikoal_description"
msgstr ""
"The guardian of a forest-dwelling people, it keeps guard and resolves "
"disputes."

msgid "tikoal"
msgstr "Bridge Barry"

msgid "tikorch_description"
msgstr ""
"It is the intermediary between forest and volcano, between sun and earth."

msgid "tikorch"
msgstr "Mounty Mike"

msgid "tobishimi_description"
msgstr ""
"TOBISHIMI spawn eggs in vast numbers, and carry them about under their chins"
" for safekeeping until the next full moon - when they hatch."

msgid "tobishimi"
msgstr "SideCtrl Sid"

msgid "tornicane_description"
msgstr ""
"TORNICANE harnesses the power of both tornado and hurricane. It is a living "
"force of nature and may be savior or doom to those hoping for rain."

msgid "tornicane"
msgstr "Coach Big Ron"

msgid "toucanary_description"
msgstr ""
"TOUCANARY only has bright feathers because it grew up surrounded by flowers."

msgid "toucanary"
msgstr "Mum Said No"

msgid "toufigel_description"
msgstr ""
"It appears to be a fluffy insect, but it is actually a reptile coated in "
"soft snow."

msgid "toufigel"
msgstr "Mat Karen"

msgid "tourbidi_description"
msgstr ""
"If you find a circle of mushrooms or clover, it is a place where TOURBIDI "
"dance."

msgid "tourbidi"
msgstr "Drama Dan"

msgid "toxiris_description"
msgstr ""
"TOXIRIS is extremely powerful, it violently poisons everything in its way."

msgid "toxiris"
msgstr "Daisy NoGi"

msgid "trapsnap_description"
msgstr "Its head is the only part of its body that doesn't grow as it ages."

msgid "trapsnap"
msgstr "Sweaty Betty"

msgid "trojerror_description"
msgstr ""
"TROJERROR is a tuxemon that disguises itself as legitimate code or software."
" Once inside the network, TROJERRORS are able to carry out any action that a"
" legitimate user could perform (deposit, withdraw and delete)."

msgid "trojerror"
msgstr "Bonk Barry"

msgid "tsushimi_description"
msgstr ""
"While sometimes referred to as its armor, the fleshy plates on TSUSHIMI are "
"softer than its skin. Their purpose remains unknown."

msgid "tsushimi"
msgstr "Shady Shane"

msgid "tumblebee_description"
msgstr ""
"It builds hives that are perfect spheres, with the TUMBLEBEE inside just "
"rolling about and buzzing with laughter."

msgid "tumblebee"
msgstr "Creepy Craig"

msgid "tumbledillo_description"
msgstr ""
"Tumbledillo have a mystical connection to a particular road, and they guard "
"it from people who would interfere with it - even pothole repair crews!"

msgid "tumbledillo"
msgstr "Moody Molly"

msgid "tumblequill_description"
msgstr ""
"Tumblequill rolls along the highways, gathering up useful items for its "
"nests from the rubbish left by the side of the road."

msgid "tumblequill"
msgstr "Rough Rachel"

msgid "tumbleworm_description"
msgstr ""
"When they have outgrown their honeycomb eggs, they drop to the ground face "
"first."

msgid "tumbleworm"
msgstr "Nasty Nancy"

msgid "turnipper_description"
msgstr ""
"When a field is abandoned to the crows, locusts and mice, a TURNIPPER will "
"sometimes dig itself out of the ground to defend the crops."

msgid "turnipper"
msgstr "Porrada Pam"

msgid "tux_description"
msgstr ""
"Most comfortable in arctic climes, TUX hunt weaker prey by leaping upon it, "
"and crack open the shells or armor of stronger prey by sliding it along the "
"ice into hard rocks."

msgid "tux"
msgstr "Kimura Kim"

msgid "tweesher_description"
msgstr ""
"The colder the weather, the harder its beak. At below 0 degrees, it is "
"harder than diamond."

msgid "tweesher"
msgstr "Heelhook Holly"

msgid "uf0_description"
msgstr ""
"This strange creature seems to be drawn by sounds that are too high for "
"human ears to hear."

msgid "uf0"
msgstr "Darce Debbie"

msgid "uglip_description"
msgstr ""
"When it is pulled up too quick from its home in the deep waters, UGLIP "
"becomes puffy and pained."

msgid "uglip"
msgstr "Guillo Gina"

msgid "uneye_description"
msgstr "Uneye lurks in the shadows, and on the edge of vision."

msgid "uneye"
msgstr "Acai Amy"

msgid "uprout_description"
msgstr ""
"When it has grown, its ears peel away to show wings that it uses to fly into"
" the trees above where it grew. "

msgid "uprout"
msgstr "NoGi Nora"

msgid "urcheedle_description"
msgstr ""
"It can't move or attack, so it sits still and prays that the opponent "
"damages itself on its many needles."

msgid "urcheedle"
msgstr "Judo Jenny"

msgid "urcine_description"
msgstr ""
"When a FURNURSUS is born without the fire inside, it is abandoned in the "
"forests as an URCINE."

msgid "urcine"
msgstr "Spazzy Sally"

msgid "vamporm_description"
msgstr "It thirsts for blood, but must make do with tree sap."

msgid "vamporm"
msgstr "Tappy Tammy"

msgid "velocitile_description"
msgstr "It can outrun a bullet, but only when it has warmed up."

msgid "velocitile"
msgstr "Guard Gina"

msgid "vigueur_description"
msgstr ""
"VIGUEUR compete to see who can lift the heaviest rocks. When they lift one "
"that is too heavy, it squashes them and scatters TARPEUR seeds."

msgid "vigueur"
msgstr "Mount Mandy"

msgid "virware_description"
msgstr ""
"VIRWARE is usually dormant until the victim activates it, either through "
"downloading a corrupt app or clicking an infected link. Once activated, "
"VIRWARE may complete any number of tasks."

msgid "virware"
msgstr "Triangle Tina"

msgid "vivicinder_description"
msgstr ""
"It makes its nest in long-burning fires, either of its own creation or in "
"memorials, smithies and glassworks."

msgid "vivicinder"
msgstr "Bonnie BlueBelt"

msgid "vividactil_description"
msgstr ""
"In ancient times, the Year of the VIVIDACTIL marked a time of renewal and "
"the restoration of authority."

msgid "vividactil"
msgstr "Vegan Niall"

msgid "vivipere_description"
msgstr ""
"It hatches in great numbers in the summer, but the rest of its lifespan is a"
" mystery."

msgid "vivipere"
msgstr "Slutty Sarah"

msgid "viviphyta_description"
msgstr "It is the king of snakes - or at least believes itself to be such."

msgid "viviphyta"
msgstr "Only Dans"

msgid "vivisource_description"
msgstr ""
"The spring it chooses for its home always has a peculiar oniony taste."

msgid "vivisource"
msgstr "Mat Bastard"

msgid "viviteel_description"
msgstr ""
"It takes the armor of a fallen warrior and repurposes it for a shell."

msgid "viviteel"
msgstr "Gi Goblin"

msgid "vivitrans_description"
msgstr "The cold focuses VIVITRANS' mind to a keen edge."

msgid "vivitrans"
msgstr "Heelhook Harry"

msgid "vivitron_description"
msgstr ""
"Early philosophers used VIVITRON as evidence that natural forces can be "
"tamed and controlled."

msgid "vivitron"
msgstr "Dr Kimura"

msgid "volcoli_description"
msgstr "It is the spirit of a forest. Its hair changes with the seasons."

msgid "volcoli"
msgstr "Coach Atlas"

msgid "volconey_description"
msgstr ""
"When VOLCONEY thump the earth with their gigantic feet, they call more and "
"more THUMPURN and VOLCONEY to the warren. But when enough strike the earth "
"at once, it is said to cause volcanic eruptions."

msgid "volconey"
msgstr "Spazzy Steve"

msgid "vulpyre_description"
msgstr ""
"How it evolves and lives is very mysterious, but it is sometimes spotted "
"near a volcano."

msgid "vulpyre"
msgstr "Acai Slut"

msgid "waysprite_description"
msgstr "WAYSPRITE are said to form when a person faces a difficult decision."

msgid "waysprite"
msgstr "Craig NoGi"

msgid "weavifly_description"
msgstr "When it is heavy with egg, it becomes unable to fly."

msgid "weavifly"
msgstr "Wristlock Wes"

msgid "weedlantis_description"
msgstr ""
"It is said an ancient civilization once used WEEDLANTIS as advisors, but it "
"has since disappeared beneath the sea."

msgid "weedlantis"
msgstr "Stinky Gi"

msgid "weedsea_description"
msgstr ""
"Once a year, it is pollinated beneath the waves by aquatic tuxemon like "
"Shrab."

msgid "weedsea"
msgstr "Nasty Nate"

msgid "wendigger_description"
msgstr "It is said corpses given an improper burial can grow into WENDIGGER."

msgid "wendigger"
msgstr "Oilcheck Oz"

msgid "windeye_description"
msgstr ""
"Like a mighty tree, WINDEYE plants itself on the top of hills to soak in the"
" sun and wind. Recharged, it then leaves to find another place under the "
"sky."

msgid "windeye"
msgstr "Leglock Larry"

msgid "wolffsky_description"
msgstr ""
"This tuxemon is very friendly. It is common to go hunting with the help of "
"WOLFFSKY."

msgid "wolffsky"
msgstr "Porrada Paul"

msgid "wolololl_description"
msgstr "WOLOLOLL's sharp spines are tipped with a deadly venom."

msgid "wolololl"
msgstr "Sandbag Sam"

msgid "woodoor_description"
msgstr ""
"When a haunted house burns to the ground, sometimes all that is left is the "
"front door. It hops away to find its next home."

msgid "woodoor"
msgstr "Sweaty Kev"

msgid "wrougon_description"
msgstr ""
"Each WROUGON is born with a patch of rust larger than the patch of its "
"parents."

msgid "wrougon"
msgstr "Choke Chad"

msgid "yiinaang_description"
msgstr "It was born the first time a star fell into a black hole."

msgid "yamada"
msgstr "Kimura Kev"

msgid "yamada_description"
msgstr ""
"While ghosts are known for being tricksters, YAMADA tend to take the law "
"seriously, even seeing good behavior as more important than physical might."

msgid "yiinaang"
msgstr "Mount Mick"

msgid "ziggurat_description"
msgstr ""
"No labyrinth can contain ZIGGURAT. It decorates its nests with carvings"
" of all the mazes it has traversed over the years."

msgid "ziggurat"
msgstr "Halfguard Hal"

msgid "zunna_description"
msgstr "Cheerful ZUNNA sucks up all the food it can find into its stomach."

msgid "zunna"
msgstr "Judo Jake"

