msgid "spyder_walled_midas2"
msgstr ""
"... ... ...\n"
" I founded the Walled Garden as a sanctuary for the better class of person\n"
" to hone their battle skills and network with fellow members of the elite.\n"
" But seeing you, a...\n"
" what is the word?\n"
" I want to say 'hoi polloi'? 'Villein'?\n"
" Seeing a pleb like you triumph has made me reconsider.\n"
" From this day on, I am going to open the Walled Garden to all comers.\n"
" Anyone who wants to test their mettle can do so here."

msgid "spyder_cottonhouse1_tvwatch"
