msgid "eclipse_route7_sylvester1"
msgstr "The sea is a long way from here."

msgid "eclipse_route7_fritz1"
msgstr ""
"A typical Crystal breakfast consists of white sausage, wheat beer and "
"pretzels."

msgid "eclipse_route7_statius1"
msgstr "What would you change about yourself if you could change one thing?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_statius2"
msgstr "Probably my party, monsters party."

msgid "eclipse_route7_jacopo1"
msgstr "Are you interested to download an app?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_jacopo2"
msgstr "The app matches zombies with victims."

msgid "eclipse_route7_pia1"
msgstr "Are you really going to ignore me?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_pia2"
msgstr "After everything that happened during this fight?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_penitent1"
msgstr ""
"The chocolate chip cookies smelled so good that I ate one without asking."

msgid "eclipse_route7_penitent2"
msgstr "Please, don't tell anyone!"

msgid "eclipse_route7_nino1"
msgstr "I enjoyed the peacefulness of nature on the mountain bushwalk."

msgid "eclipse_route7_nino2"
msgstr "Not so peaceful!"

msgid "eclipse_route7_hugh1"
msgstr "Do you mind if I smoke?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_hugh2"
msgstr "How to quit?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_arnaut1"
msgstr ""
"The bad thing about inferiority complexes is that the wrong people have "
"them."

msgid "eclipse_route7_arnaut2"
msgstr "Oops!"

msgid "eclipse_route7_conrad1"
msgstr "The Lion Mountain got snow, and all the tourists are very excited."

msgid "eclipse_route7_conrad2"
msgstr "Too many tourists."

msgid "eclipse_route7_manfred1"
msgstr "Do you think our lives will ever go back to normal?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_manfred2"
msgstr "I mean... after Cotton Town."

msgid "eclipse_route7_sordello1"
msgstr "If you could buy anything you wanted, what would you buy?"

msgid "eclipse_route7_sordello2"
msgstr "Probably a couple of revives and some potions."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_alert_skating"
msgstr "Always be cautious! Always bring safety gear!"

msgid "eclipse_crystal_hackerchat"
msgstr "Two weeks ago a tremendous blizzard struck ${{map_name}}."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_barmaid"
msgstr "I don't skate very well."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_grannypiper"
msgstr ""
"The Great Blizzard's impact was so great that, still today, survivors met to"
" commemorate."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_monk"
msgstr "I'm reminded of the time the blizzard killed my friend."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_granny"
msgstr "That's, uh... heavy. I'm sorry to hear that."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_shopkeeper"
msgstr ""
"We worship and have deep respect for the mountain, we trust it will save us "
"from whatever comes."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_maniac"
msgstr ""
"Climbers need to wake up and understand that climbing Lion Mountain is extremely risky.\n"
"They need to stop believing just because they have strong tuxemon that they will be able to climb."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_beck"
msgstr "That's not even a little bit funny, buddy."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_tvwatch"
msgstr "A journalist travels the globe hunting for lost civilizations."

