msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_jacques1"
msgstr ""
"I've never been that high before \n"
" and it's very very strenuous to climb ice like that."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_jacques2"
msgstr ""
"Not only is it technically difficult and unstable and frightening \n"
" but your heart goes like crazy because of the altitude."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_adam1"
msgstr "I was up, it was windy."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_adam2"
msgstr "Then it started snowing."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_arlene1"
msgstr "No anchors at any point."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_arlene2"
msgstr "It was physically very, very tiring, full-body climbing really."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_david1"
msgstr ""
"It took me the best part of five or six hours to climb about the last piece."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_david2"
msgstr "Carried on way after it got dark."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_alexander1"
msgstr "Already the clouds are coming in from the east. Big clouds."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_alexander2"
msgstr "I expect this ridge to be quite ... Brace yourself."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_emilio1"
msgstr "Half an hour to an hour after leaving the summit, I was lost."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_emilio2"
msgstr "I was in the wild, I couldn't see anything."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_chhurim1"
msgstr "I'm going to make the summit, I can actually make the summit."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_chhurim2"
msgstr "Will there be anyone there?"

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_tom1"
msgstr "I don't know entirely what happened for the rest of that night."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_tom2"
msgstr ""
"I stopped looking at the watch, and everything just started to go apart."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_conrad1"
msgstr "I remember smelling something."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_conrad2"
msgstr "It was a really strong smell."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_kurt1"
msgstr "I'm not capable of going any further."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_kurt2"
msgstr "I made the mistake of having a little bit of hope."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_snarlon1"
msgstr "Graar!"

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_snarlon2"
msgstr "Ufff."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_nurse1"
msgstr "To be honest with you, I am older than you think."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_scientist1"
msgstr "That's the biggest grasshopper I've ever seen."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_enforcer1"
msgstr "So the incident at the Datacenter has been resolved?"

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_enforcer2"
msgstr ""
"It could have been so much worse.\n"
" Omnichannel was developing a tuxemon that can control human emotion.\n"
" If Kernel had gotten access to Chromeye, there would have been no stopping it."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_enforcer3"
msgstr "So when the breakdown occurred, I retreated here."

msgid "eclipse_lionmountain_enforcer4"
msgstr ""
"It looks like you can handle this. Maybe you are the only one who can."

msgid "eclipse_bank_may"
msgstr "May"

msgid "eclipse_bank_brock"
msgstr "Brock"

msgid "eclipse_bank_daisy"
msgstr "Daisy"

msgid "eclipse_bank_raj"
msgstr "Raj"

msgid "eclipse_bank_lile"
msgstr "Lile"

msgid "eclipse_bank_kai"
msgstr "Kai"

msgid "eclipse_bank_ethan"
msgstr "Ethan"

msgid "eclipse_bank_ava"
msgstr "Ava"

msgid "eclipse_bank_lucas"
msgstr "Lucas"

msgid "eclipse_bank_bob1"
msgstr "I used to think this bank stood for somethingâ€”independence, a beacon against the Cathedral's shadow."

msgid "eclipse_bank_bob2"
msgstr "But then I saw cracks: strange transfers, unaccounted funds, whispers of deals with Cathedral subsidiaries."

msgid "eclipse_bank_bob3"
msgstr "They let me go when I started asking questions. Something's not right here, Argon. Not at all."

msgid "eclipse_bank_may1"
msgstr "Think you can handle high finance? Prove it."

msgid "eclipse_bank_may2"
msgstr "You've got the chops. But I won't sit quietly if things fall apart."

msgid "eclipse_bank_brock1"
msgstr "You ask too many questions. Let's see if you can back it up."

msgid "eclipse_bank_brock2"
msgstr "You're tougher than I expected. But I'll be tightening security from now on."

msgid "eclipse_bank_daisy1"
msgstr "Troublemakers don't last long here. Let's see what you've got."

msgid "eclipse_bank_daisy2"
msgstr "You're formidable, I'll give you that. But trust? That's earned, not won."

msgid "eclipse_bank_jeff1"
msgstr "This place looks cleanâ€”but I've seen the dirt beneath. You ready to dig?"

msgid "eclipse_bank_bin1"
msgstr "You find a crumpled receipt: 'Archipelago Freight - Lumber shipment to Fondent Region (Confidential).'"

msgid "eclipse_bank_bin2"
msgstr "Below it, a document stamped 'TerraForm Developers - Prototype facility construction (Project Eclipse).'"

msgid "eclipse_bank_bin3"
msgstr "A torn note scribbled hastily reads: 'Meet J at powerplant. Discuss energy output. Eyes everywhere. Don't get caught.'"

msgid "eclipse_bank_raj1"
msgstr "I'm just here to deposit my checkâ€”but this place feels ready to explode."

msgid "eclipse_bank_raj2"
msgstr "You're braver than I thought. Just be carefulâ€”this bank's secrets run deep."

msgid "eclipse_bank_lile1"
msgstr "I've spotted patterns pointing to Cathedral. Help me test a theoryâ€”if you're up for it."

msgid "eclipse_bank_lile2"
msgstr "You've proven yourself. Now let's expose the strings Cathedral's pulling behind the scenes."

msgid "eclipse_bank_kai1"
msgstr "The records don't lieâ€”unless someone makes them. Let's see if you can handle the truth."

msgid "eclipse_bank_kai2"
msgstr "You've got grit. I'll share what I've foundâ€”but tread carefully. Cathedral doesn't like leaks."

msgid "eclipse_bank_ethan1"
msgstr "TuxeVault's books are spotlessâ€”too spotless. Let's see if you can crack the polish."

msgid "eclipse_bank_ethan2"
msgstr "You've got guts. Maybe you're the one who'll finally expose the lies beneath the numbers."

msgid "eclipse_bank_ava1"
msgstr "I've flagged suspicious flows. If you care about truth, prove you're not just another pawn."

msgid "eclipse_bank_ava2"
msgstr "You've got more to you than meets the eye. Just rememberâ€”Cathedral doesn't play fair."

msgid "eclipse_bank_lucas1"
msgstr "You've got guts coming here. I can make you richâ€”if you're not afraid to get dirty."

msgid "eclipse_bank_lucas2"
msgstr "So you're not interested in deals? Fine. But don't expect to walk away untouched."

msgid "eclipse_zircon"
msgstr "Zircon"

msgid "eclipse_zircon1"
msgstr "So, you finally show your face, Argon. I've been waiting for this moment. Let's see if your ideals can stand against true power."

msgid "eclipse_zircon2_lose"
msgstr "Pathetic, Argon. Is this the strength your so-called principles bring you? You can't protect anyoneâ€”least of all yourself.\n Remember this defeat. It's the only thing you've truly earned."

msgid "eclipse_zircon_voice_lose"
msgstr "Voice of Revelation: You've tasted defeat, Argon, and now the pieces begin to fall. Aurora's disappearance is no accident...\n Nor is your survival. The path ahead is darker than you know, but you must walk it.\n Watch the Cathedral. Watch the mountains. The truth waits for you... if you dare to see it."

msgid "eclipse_zircon2_win"
msgstr "Impossibleâ€¦ You cling to ideals, and yet you stand. Perhaps I underestimated what conviction can become."

msgid "eclipse_zircon3_win"
msgstr "Don't mistake technical victory for narrative control, Argon. The endgame has already begun."

msgid "eclipse_zircon_voice_win"
msgstr "Voice of Revelation: You've defied power, Argonâ€”and now the veil begins to lift. Aurora's trail is not cold.\n The Cathedral watches, but so do others. The truth is moving. Follow it before it disappears."

msgid "eclipse_cathedral_jada1"
msgstr "Ah, you're finally awake. Took quite a hit from that... Scientist Zircon? He was a guest hereâ€”an intimidating fellow, but an honored one.\n Don't worry, the Cathedral is thorough; we got you stabilized."

msgid "eclipse_cathedral_jada2"
msgstr "As for the bank... a terrible commotion. They say CEO Aurora disappeared right after the fight. Vanished without a trace.\n The authorities are calling it a 'crisis of confidence'. That's all I know."

msgid "eclipse_cathedral_jada3"
msgstr "You sound agitated. Just be careful what you say, Argon. These walls have ears, and the Cathedral doesn't like loose ends.\n Focus on recovering."

msgid "eclipse_event10_1"
msgstr "Zircon... Cathedral... Aurora. He spoke of results, and now Aurora is a casualty. They used me to create a distraction.\n I need to find her, and expose them."

msgid "eclipse_event10_2"
msgstr "Voice of Doubt: It's too big, Argon. They'll crush you and your ideals like they crushed Chrome Robo. Walk away before they bury you too."

msgid "eclipse_event10_3"
msgstr "Voice of Compassion: Aurora fought for TuxeVault's independence, against the five pillars of the Cathedral.\n She was fighting for something real. You can't let them erase her."

msgid "eclipse_event10_4"
msgstr "Voice of Revelation: The path ahead is darker than you know. Aurora's disappearance is no accident... nor is your survival.\n Watch the Cathedral. Watch the mountains. The truth waits for you... if you dare to see it."

msgid "eclipse_event10_5"
msgstr "The Cathedral and the mountains. The hidden facility must be there, tied to Project Eclipse.\n I'll follow the trail to Lion Mountain. I won't run this time."

msgid "eclipse_cathedral_enforcer1"
msgstr "Leaving so soon, sir? The Cathedral appreciates your business.\n Just remember, in times of 'crisis', it's always safer to let the authorities handle things.\n Especially anything involving the TuxeVault CEO. Good day."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_hiker1"
msgstr "Oh, TerraForm Developers? Yeah, I know those guys. They're always hauling heavy equipment up the old path.\n That path leads to Lion Mountain Below."

msgid "eclipse_crystal_hiker2"
msgstr "They put up a huge security barrier recently, near where the old Hydro-Plant used to be, halfway up.\n They say they're building something 'prototype' up there for the Cathedral's Nimrod division.\n I wouldn't go near it."

msgid "eclipse_event11_1"
msgstr "Voice of Challenge: You chose the mountain path, Argon. It's steep, and the air is thin.\n You'll find no one up there but yourself, your Tuxemon, and the answers you truly dread. Let's see if you can still stand when the truth hits the peak."

msgid "eclipse_event12_1"
msgstr "Voice of Memory: The air here is clean, but your hands aren't, Argon.\n Every upward step is one step further from what you destroyed."

msgid "eclipse_event12_2"
msgstr "Voice of Doubt: This is a fool's errand. You're climbing a mountain built on secrets.\n You won't find Aurora; you'll only find a tomb."

msgid "eclipse_event12_3"
msgstr "Voice of Wisdom: The summit is not reached by looking at the peak, but by focusing on the next step.\n Keep moving, child."

msgid "eclipse_event13_1"
msgstr "Voice of Challenge: The path narrows here. You were overwhelmed by Zircon.\n Let's see if this climb breaks your resolve before the truth does."

msgid "eclipse_event13_2"
msgstr "Voice of Temptation: The old Hydro-Plant offered comfort and power. Turn back. Find a compromise.\n Fighting the Cathedral only leads to exhaustion."

msgid "eclipse_event13_3"
msgstr "Cold Voice: You trespass, Argon. Nimrod watches its assets closely.\n This mountain belongs to the ones with the power to take it."

msgid "eclipse_event14_1"
msgstr "Reflective Voice: Look how small the town is now. You are utterly alone here.\n If you fall, no one will know, and no one will care."

msgid "eclipse_event14_2"
msgstr "Voice of Judgment: You sought justice, but brought chaos.\n Did you truly believe your ideals would survive at this altitude? They are frozen solid."

msgid "eclipse_event14_3"
msgstr "Voice of Compassion: The air is thin, but your purpose is clear. You are close, Argon.\n Don't let the cold silence extinguish the light you carry."

msgid "eclipse_event15_1"
msgstr "Echo of the Past: We built things once, Zircon and you. Now look at what they build: mines, walls, and silence.\n Is this the result you wanted?"

msgid "eclipse_event15_2"
msgstr "Whispered Voice: Don't speak about the tunnels. Don't speak about Shaft's quotas.\n The dirt here has ears, and the guards are Nimrod's best."

msgid "eclipse_event15_3"
msgstr "Voice of Temptation: The mountain is just rock. The people are just labor.\n Everything has a price, Argon. What's yours? Shaft is hiring."

msgid "eclipse_event15_4"
msgstr "Unknown Voice: The mine is deep, but the purpose is deeper. They're not extracting minerals; they're covering tracks.\n Follow the dark earth."

msgid "eclipse_park_welcome"
msgstr ""
"Welcome to Pepper Park. Entry is ${{currency}}500. You'll get 25 Park "
"Tuxeball. Are you ready?"

