msgstr "Welcome!"

msgid "eclipse_park_guardian1"
msgstr "Do you want to interrupt your experience?"

msgid "eclipse_park_guardian2"
msgstr "Have you seen tree stumps?"

msgid "eclipse_park_guardian3"
msgstr ""
"Illegal logging. The authority's pledge to curb illegal logging exists only on paper. In reality they have not been able to stop it.\n"
"I have no faith that the authority will protect the forests and the environment. We have to take this matter into our own hands."

msgid "eclipse_park_guardian4"
msgstr "It's revolting!"

msgid "eclipse_park_guardian5"
msgstr ""
"Do you think we got sewer systems and centralized treatment plants inside a "
"park?!"

msgid "eclipse_park_nomoney"
msgstr "Unfortunately you don't have enough money!"

msgid "eclipse_park_yesmoney"
msgstr "Enjoy your experience!"

msgid "eclipse_park_steps100"
msgstr "You still have 100 steps left!"

msgid "eclipse_park_scientist1"
msgstr ""
"Many parks limit or even prohibit scientific activities, but we are at the "
"forefront of ecological knowledge!"

msgid "eclipse_park_tennisplayer1"
msgstr "Fingers crossed your next encounter is with a friendly one!"

msgid "eclipse_park_professor1"
msgstr ""
"There are fences for the visitors, but no fences around the park for the "
"monsters, and that's the way a park is supposed to be."

msgid "eclipse_park_soldier1"
msgstr ""
"I think the park has done a pretty good job of being everyone's friend."

